Florida%2C%20to%20discuss%20a%20private%20matter%2C%20according%20to%20three%20people%20briefed%20on%20the%20meeting%20who%20spoke%20on%20the%20condition%20of%20anonymity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Trump's%20aides%20have%20not%20responded%20to%20Musk's%20social%20media%20remarks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20past%2C%20Musk%20has%20contributed%20to%20both%20Republicans%20and%20Democrats%2C%20much%20like%20many%20other%20business%20titans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20not%20heavily%20invested%20in%20a%20presidential%20campaign%2C%20in%20contrast%20to%20other%20American%20billionaires%2C%20and%20over%20the%20years%2C%20he%20has%20divided%20his%20contributions%20roughly%20equally%20between%20Republicans%20and%20Democrats%2C%20according%20to%20New%20York%20Times.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20recent%20development%20regarding%20the%20US%20Presidential%20race%2C%20Republican%20candidate%2C%20Nikki%20Haley%20formally%20announced%20on%20Wednesday%20to%20end%20her%20presidential%20candidate%20campaign.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20time%20has%20now%20come%20to%20suspend%20my%20campaign.%20I%20said%20I%20wanted%20Americans%20to%20have%20their%20voices%20heard.%20I%20have%20done%20that.%20I%20have%20no%20regrets%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20Wednesday%20in%20South%20Carolina.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAlthough%20I%20will%20no%20longer%20be%20a%20candidate%2C%20I%20will%20not%20stop%20using%20my%20voice%20for%20the%20things%20I%20believe%20in%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20while%20speaking%20from%20Charleston%2C%20South%20Carolina.%20Nikki%20Haley%20congratulated%20former%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20during%20her%20announcement%20ending%20her%20presidential%20campaign%20but%20didn't%20endorse%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20all%20likelihood%2C%20Donald%20Trump%20will%20be%20the%20Republican%20nominee%20when%20our%20party%20convention%20meets%20in%20July.%20I%20congratulate%20him%20and%20wish%20him%20well.%20I%20wish%20anyone%20well%20who%20would%20be%20America's%20president.%20Our%20country%20is%20too%20precious%20to%20let%20our%20differences%20divide%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20Haley%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaley%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20now%20up%20to%20Donald%20Trump%20to%20earn%20the%20votes%20of%20those%20in%20our%20party%20and%20beyond%20it%20who%20did%20not%20support%20him.%20And%20I%20hope%20he%20does%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20report%2C%20Haley%20had%20emerged%20as%20former%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20sole%20rival%20in%20the%20Republican%20presidential%20primary%20campaign%2C%20and%20while%20he%20rolled%20to%20victory%20in%2014%20of%20the%2015%20GOP%20contests%20on%20Super%20Tuesday%2C%20she%20foiled%20a%20possible%20clean%20sweep%20by%20winning%20in%20Vermont.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAcross%20the%20Republican%20primaries%20on%20Super%20Tuesday%2C%20Haley%20won%20just%2043%20of%20the%20Republican%20delegates%2C%20while%20Trump%20won%20764.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20President%20Biden%20and%20former%20President%20Donald%20J%20Trump%20emerged%20from%20Super%20Tuesday%20having%20amassed%20huge%20delegate%20hauls%20in%20California%2C%20Texas%2C%20and%20beyond%2C%20moving%20closer%20to%20their%20parties'%20nominations%20and%20setting%20up%20a%20rematch%20for%20the%20White%20House%20in%20November.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709770500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2F4dau661g_elon-musk-reuters_625x300_13_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Felon-musk-says-he-wont-donate-to-either-us-presidential-candidate-5190952%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Tesla%20CEO%20Elon%20Musk%20announced%20on%20Wednesday%20that%20he%20has%20no%20plans%20to%20donate%20money%20to%20either%20candidate%20for%20US%20President.%22%2C%2