friends-new-york-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ein%20New%20York%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202023.%20I'd%20also%20gotten%20published%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fflanellemag.com%2Fsuit-sans-man-by-lisa-miller-for-flanelle-magazine%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFlanelle%20Magazine%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20a%20fashion%20editorial.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20life%20kept%20taking%20us%20to%20New%20York%20for%20her%20dance%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flmillerphotography.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emy%20career%20opportunities%3C%2Fa%3E.%20So%2C%20we%20started%20to%20talk%20about%20the%20possibility%20of%20living%20in%20the%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EWe%20fell%20in%20love%20with%20Park%20Slope%2C%20Brooklyn%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20family%20hold%20hands%20and%20walks%20through%20their%20lawn%20in%20front%20of%20a%20blue%20house.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65e0ca366080194819fb4aec%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Miller%20family%20at%20their%20home%20in%20Tennessee.%3Cp%3ELisa%20Miller%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20littlest%20is%20on%20the%20autism%20spectrum%2C%20and%20he%20is%20obsessed%20with%20all%20things%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgrooms-custom-suits-new-york-wedding-photos-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENew%20York%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20Statue%20of%20Liberty.%20That%20inspired%20us%20to%20visit%20New%20York%20in%202022%2C%20and%20we%20decided%20to%20stay%20out%20of%20Manhattan%20and%20get%20an%20Airbnb%20in%20Brooklyn.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20just%20happened%20to%20come%20across%20Park%20Slope.%20It%20has%20a%20family%20vibe.%20Everything%20is%20walkable%20and%20accessible%2C%20like%20in%20Manhattan%2C%20but%20just%20a%20bit%20quieter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20fell%20in%20love%20with%20the%20area.%20It%20was%20a%20good%20fit%2C%20but%20it%20wasn't%20until%20about%20a%20year%20later%20that%20we%20decided%20to%20consider%20it%20seriously.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20brought%20up%20moving%20when%20my%20daughter%20had%20officially%20decided%20not%20to%20do%20competitive%20dance.%20We%20thought%2C%20%26quot%3BWhat%20if%20we%20look%20at%20some%20opportunities%20for%20her%20that%20aren't%20in%20Tennessee%3F%26quot%3B%20Because%20if%20she%20wants%20to%20go%20that%20pre-professional%20route%2C%20she%20can't%20do%20that%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20have%20options%20for%20dancers%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwoman-renovating-brooklyn-brownstone-photos-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elive%20in%20New%20York%20City%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20we%20were%20unwilling%20to%20do%20that.%20We're%20a%20tight-knit%20family.%20So%20we%20couldn't%20imagine%20letting%20her%20go%20alone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20September%202023%2C%20we%20started%20looking%20into%20some%20opportunities%2C%20and%20she%20joined%20a%20pre-professional%20program.%20We%20decided%20if%20she's%20going%20to%20have%20this%20opportunity%2C%20why%20don't%20we%20sell%20our%20house%20and%20go%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EWe%20quickly%20sold%20our%20house%20in%20Tennessee%20and%20found%20the%20perfect%20Brooklyn%20apartment%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20market%20is%20great%20in%20the%20Knoxville%20neighborhood%20we%20lived%20in.%20We%20bought%20our%20house%20before%20the%20market%20was%20nuts%2C%20and%20we%20talked%20to%20an%20agent%20and%20found%20out%20what%20we%20could%20get%20for%20it.%20We%20had%20three%20bedrooms%20and%202.5%20baths%2C%20but%20we%20also%20used%20our%20bonus%20room%20as%20a%20bedroom.%20Plus%2C%20we%20converted%20our%20garage%20into%20a%20studio.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20thought%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20we%20can%20make%20this%20happen%20quickly%20and%20get%20the%20profit%20off%20of%20our%20house%20that%20we%20think%20we%20can%2C%20this%20would%20be%20a%20great%20nest%20egg%20for%20us%20and%20give%20us%20that%20security%20to%20start%20over%20in%20a%20very%20expensive%20city.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20put%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Femma-stone-selling-home-in-la-photos-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehouse%20on%20the%20market%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20it%20went%20quickly.%20We%20listed%20our%20home%20on%20October%206%2C%20and%20it%20was%20under%20contract%20by%20October%208.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20lease%20in%20Park%20Slope%20started%20in%20November%20because%20we%20found%20the%20perfect%20apartment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20looked%20on%20StreetEasy%2C%20and%20I%20set%20up%20a%20lot%20of%20search%20parameters%20that%20it%20would%20email%20me%20when%20something%20came%20on%20the%20market.%20We%20were%20thinking%20we'd%20end%20up%20in%20a%20three-bedroom.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20friend%20I%20made%20on%20a%20Facebook%20group%20local%20to%20our%20neighborhood%20sent%20me%20a%20listing%20for%20a%20four-bedroom%2C%20two-bathroom%20apartment.%20We%20originally%20planned%20for%20my%20boys%20to%20share%20because%20they%20are%20only%2014%20months%20apart%2C%20but%20then%20we%20found%20this%20place%20in%20our%20price%20range.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20jumped%20on%20it%20after%20a%20virtual%20tour.%20We%20talked%20to%20the%20agent%2C%20and%20two%20days%20later%2C%20they%20had%20our%20money%2C%20and%20our%20lease%20was%20signed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20family%20of%20five%20stand%20in%20front%20of%20the%20Brooklyn%20Bridge.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65e0c9dc6080194819fb4a9f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Miller%20family%20in%20Brooklyn%20in%202022.%3Cp%3ELisa%20Miller%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20totally%20nervous%20about%20it%2C%20but%20the%20agent%20did%20a%20good%20job%20of%20walking%20me%20through%20the%20property.%20I%20asked%20a%20lot%20of%20questions.%20We%20spoke%20to%20th