e%20on%20our%20side.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMickey%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20You%20need%20someone%20who%20knows%20all%20the%20laws%2C%20especially%20regarding%20mortgages.%20That's%20why%20it%20was%20great%20to%20have%20him.%20Every%20time%20I%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20mortgage%20company%20told%20me%20I%20can't%20get%20the%20loan%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20would%20remind%20them%20of%20my%20legal%20rights%20and%20they'd%20get%20the%20job%20done.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGrace%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20We%20would%20not%20have%20been%20able%20to%20really%20understand%20the%20process%20and%20close%20our%20loan%20without%20Mark%20and%20our%20attorney%2C%20Paul.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EWe're%20the%20youngest%20homeowners%20in%20our%20family%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMickey%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EI%20always%20wanted%20to%20reach%20this%20point%20in%20my%20life%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhousing-market-home-price-outlook-prediction-financial-crisis-meredith-whitney-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebecome%20a%20homeowner%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20just%20wasn't%20sure%20it%20would%20happen.%20And%20now%20that%20it%20has%2C%20it%20still%20doesn't%20feel%20real.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGrace%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWe%20say%20it%20all%20the%20time%2C%20but%20we%20can't%20even%20believe%20this%20is%20our%20home.%20We%20wanted%20to%20invest%20in%20something%20within%20ourselves%20and%20each%20other%2C%20and%20we%20worked%20really%20hard%20to%20get%20here.%20It's%20such%20a%20huge%20accomplishment%20for%20us.%20We're%20young%2C%20in%20our%20early%2020s%2C%20and%20the%20youngest%20homebuyers%20in%20both%20of%20our%20families.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Grace%20Lucchese%20and%20Mickey%20Ricard's%20living%20room.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65e8b3136080194819fd24bc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20couple's%20living%20room.%3Cp%3