2%80%94%20the%20Pittsburgh-based%20Arias%20Organization.%20News%20of%20the%20subpoenas%20was%20detailed%20in%20an%20internal%20Globe%20document%20obtained%20by%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Business%20Insider%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fglobe-life-insurance-lawsuit-american-income-arias-agency-toxic-workplace-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Earticles%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fglobe-life-arias-under-investigation-after-allegations-of-fraud-sexual-abuse-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epublished%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feeoc-takes-up-sexual-harassment-cases-against-globe-life-subsidiary-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E2023%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20former%20agents%20described%20a%20culture%20at%20Arias%20of%20customer%20abuses%20and%20sexual%20harassment%2C%20including%20multiple%20allegations%20of%20sexual%20assault%20on%20the%20job.%20One%20former%20agent%2C%20Renee%20Zinsky%2C%20filed%20suit%20claiming%20her%20boss%2C%20Michael%20Russin%2C%20had%20sexually%20assaulted%20her%20in%20his%20car%20numerous%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20internal%20document%2C%20written%20by%20Joel%20Scarborough%2C%20Globe's%20general%20counsel%20for%20its%20insurance%20subsidiaries%2C%20said%20the%20subpoenas%20seek%20information%20about%20internal%20investigations%2C%20life%20insurance%20policyholders%2C%20customer%20payment%20information%2C%20and%20files%20about%20insurance%20policies%20written%20in%202022%20by%20Arias.%20Trina%20Orlando%2C%20a%20spokesperson%20for%20Arias%2C%20declined%20to%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20BI%20described%20the%20Scarborough%20document%20to%20Cathy%20Seifert%2C%20a%20securities%20analyst%20at%20CFRA%20Research%2C%20Seifert%20said%20she%20will%20be%20watching%20how%20management%20addresses%20the%20DOJ%20subpoenas%20to%20its%20investors.%20%26quot%3BIf%20Globe%20does%20not%20adequately%2C%20clearly%20and%20honestly%20disclose%20not%20only%20the%20problem%20but%20the%20nature%20of%20the%20problem%2C%20then%20all%20of%20a%20sudden%20you%20not%20only%20have%20the%20DOJ%2C%20but%20you%20will%20have%20the%20Securities%20and%20Exchange%20Commission%20involved%20as%20well%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20disclosures.%26quot%3B%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EGlobe%20Life%20executives%20made%20no%20mention%20of%20the%20DOJ%20probe%20during%20a%20quarterly%20earnings%20call%20on%20February%208.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20January%2022%2C%20Globe%20sent%20an%20email%20with%20the%20Scarborough%20attachment%20to%20an%20unspecified%20AIL%20%26quot%3BDistribution%20List%2C%26quot%3B%20instructing%20recipients%20to%20preserve%20documents%20related%20to%20the%20DOJ's%20orders.%20Scarborough%20wrote%20that%20the%20US%20Attorney's%20Office%20for%20the%20Western%20District%20of%20Pennsylvania%20had%20sent%20subpoenas%20to%20Globe%20and%20AIL%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20DOJ%20and%20told%20people%20to%20hold%20onto%20records%20related%20to%20Arias%20and%20six%20of%20its%20current%20and%20former%20leaders%20and%20staff%2C%20including%20agency%20owner%20Simon%20Arias%3B%20his%20executive%20assistant%20Natalie%20Price%3B%20and%20Russin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20consequences%20of%20violating%20the%20duty%20to%20preserve%20documents%20may%20be%20very%20serious%2C%26quot%3B%20Scarborough%20wrote.%20In%20the%20document%2C%20he%20directed%20recipients%20to%20preserve%20any%20email%2C%20texts%2C%20or%20other%20communications%20related%20to%20Arias%20Agencies%20or%20any%20of%20the%20leaders%20who%20were%20named.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Department%20of%20Justice%20declined%20to%20comment.%20A%20spokeswoman%20for%20Globe%20and%20AIL%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20inquiries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20DOJ%20probe%20is%20just%20the%20latest%20blow%20to%20the%20company.%20Warren%20Buffett's%20Berkshire%20Hathaway%20owned%206.35%20million%20shares%20of%20Globe%20when%20BI%20began%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fglobe-life-insurance-lawsuit-american-income-arias-agency-toxic-workplace-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einvestigative%20series%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20company%20and%20its%20subsidiaries%20a%20year%20ago.%20He%20has%20since%20sold%20all%20of%20his%20Globe%20shares.%20In%20October%2C%20insurance%20regulators%20in%20Pennsylvania%20fined%20American%20Income%20Life%20%24130%2C000%20for%20engaging%20in%20deceptive%20consumer%20practices.%20Arias%20Agencies%20was%20not%20named%20in%20the%20consent%20decree%20in%20that%20case%2C%20but%20it%20operates%20half%20of%20AIL's%20Pennsylvania%20offices.%20In%20November%2C%20the%20Equal%20Employment%20Opportunity%20Commission%20said%20it%20was%20reopening%20two%20sexual%20harassment%20cases%20against%20AIL%20that%20it%20had%20previously%20dismissed%2C%20an%20unusual%20move%20for%20the%20agency.%20One%20of%20the%20two%20cases%20was%20Zinsky's.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20the%20Department%20of%20Justice%20appears%20to%20be%20conducting%20its%20own%20investigation%20into%20possible%20abuses%20of%20customers%20with%20its%20broad%20requests%20for%20policyholder%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBI%20was%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fglobe-life-insurance-lawsuit-american-income-arias-agency-toxic-workplace-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efirst%20to%20write%20about%3C%2Fa%3E%20allegations%20of%20widespread%20customer%20abuses%20at%20Arias%2C%20including%20increasing%20premiums%20without%20customers'%20knowledge%2C%20pushing%20products%20on%20people%20in%20financial%20straits%2C%20and%20forging%20customers'%20signatures.%20Several%20former%20agents%20previously%20told%20BI%20they%20saw%20colleagues%20write%20up%20policies%20in%20the%20names%20of%20dead%20people%20and%20take%20mouth%20swabs%20for%20people%20who%20smoked%20in%20order%20to%20get%20them%20lower%20rates%20on%20policies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUp%20to%20now%2C%20Globe%20has%20said%20little%20about%20BI's%20investigations.%20But%20during%20the%20earnings%20call%20on%20February%208%2C%20James%20Darden%2C%20Globe's%20co-chief%20executive%20officer%2C%20said%20that%20%26quot%3Ban%20online%20publication%26quot%3B%20had%20posted%20articles%20related%20to%20legal%20cases%20against%20AIL%20and%20one%20of%20its%20state%20general%20agents%2C%20apparently%20referring%20to%20Arias.%20Darden%20said%20that%20he%20would%20not%20be%20taking%20questions%20on%20the%20matter%2C%20but%20that%20AIL%20%26quot%3Bvigorously%26quot%3B%20disputes%20the%20allegations.%20%26quot%3BWe%20do%20not%20believe%20the%20litigation%20will%20be%20material%20to%20Globe%20Life's%20overall%20results%20or%20American%20Income%20Life's%20agency%20operations%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDarden%20told%20the%20analysts%20that%20%26quot%3Bas%20soon%20as%20American%20Income%20became%20aware%20of%26quot%3B%20the%20allegations%2C%20AIL%20hired%20an%20outside%20investigator%20to%20look%20into%20the%20matter.%20(AIL%20hired%20the%20investigator%20in%20November%202021.%20Zinsky%20had%20spoken%20with%20Simon%20Arias%20about%20Russin's%20behavior%20three%20months%20before%20that%2C%20in%20August%202021%2C%20but%20AIL%20has%20said%20that%20it%20was%20unaware%20of%20the%20complaints%20until%20Zinsky%20reached%20out%20to%20the%20company%20directly%2C%20that%20November.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20investigator%2C%20attorney%20Janet%20Hendrick%20of%20the%20Phillips%20Murrah%20law%20firm%20in%20Dallas%2C%20was%20%26quot%3Ba%20neutral%20and%20independent%20third-party%20investigator%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20an%20email%20that%20an%20AIL%20lawyer%20sent%20to%20Zinsky%20in%20late%202021.%20Despite%20the%20claim%20of%20neutrality%20and%20independence%2C%20another%20attorney%20from%20the%20same%20firm%2C%20Kathryn%20D.%20Terry%2C%20later%20represented%20Globe%20and%20AIL%20against%20Zinsky%20after%20she%20filed%20a%20charge%20against%20them%20with%20the%20EEOC.%20Neither%20Phillips%20Murrah%20attorney%20responded%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E%26quot%3BThe%20same%20firm%20cannot%20be%20both%20the%20investigator%20and%20defense%20counsel%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Liz%20Rita%2C%20a%20senior%20attorney%20investigator%20at%20Investigations%20Law%20Group%2C%20a%20Denver%20firm%20that%20conducts%20workplace%20investigations.%20%26quot%3BThe%20investigator%20has%20to%20be%20truly%20separate%20and%20independent%20from%20counsel%2C%20or%20the%20whole%20process%20is%20tainted.%26quot%3B%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E%3Cem%3EIf%20you%20work%20at%20AIL%20and%20have%20information%20to%20share%20about%20the%20company%2C%20please%20contact%20Susan%20Antilla%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Asusan.antilla1%40gmail.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Esusan.antilla1%40gmail.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdepartment-of-justice-probe-globe-life-american-income-life-2024-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709760622000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65e897b390413ab8e1d9b5fc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdepartment-of-justice-probe-globe-life-american-income-life-2024-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Employees%20were%20alerted%20about%20the%20subpoenas%20in%20January%2C%20according%20to%20an%20internal%20email%2C%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20a%20Business%20Insider%20investigation.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22susan.antilla15%40gmail.com%20(Susan%20Antilla)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdepartment-of-justice-probe-globe-life-american-income-life-2024-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Houthi%20attack%20on%20ship%20kills%202%2C%20Indian%20Navy%20joins%20rescue%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709760512000%2C%22visual%22%3