%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhousing-market-outlook-analysis-prices-rising-extreme-weather-risk-jpmorgan-2024-2%5C%22%3Eclimate%20risks%20may%20impact%20housing%20stability%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20Deputy%20Treasury%20Secretary%20Wally%20Adeyemo%20outlined%20in%20a%20related%20blog%20post.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20working%20with%20federal%20and%20state%20regulators%20studying%20rising%20insurance%20costs%20and%20decreasing%20insurance%20coverage%20so%20that%20we%20can%20understand%20the%20impact%20of%20lack%20of%20affordable%20insurance%20on%20housing%20supply%20in%20different%20parts%20of%20the%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20moment%2C%20the%20Treasury%20lacks%20granular%20data%20on%20where%20homeowners%20are%20being%20hit%20hardest%2C%20and%20where%20insurers%20are%20pulling%20back%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faffordable-housing-solutions-billions-unused-covid-aid-treasury-department-2024-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709758138000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65e8c6cbce7f1785b2e705ff%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faffordable-housing-solutions-billions-unused-covid-aid-treasury-department-2024-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Treasury%20Department%20has%20freed%20up%20funds%20from%20COVID-era%20programs%20to%20support%20national%20housing%20projects.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22fdemott%40insider.com%20(Filip%20De%20Mott)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A15%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faffordable-housing-solutions-billions-unused-covid-aid-treasury-department-2024-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Homi%20reveals%20Sara-Saif%20have%20bizarre%20dark%20humour%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709757431000%2C%22v