ted%20bulk%20bag%20hard%20candy%20flavors%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3E%3Cstrong%3EInstant%20drink%20mix%20packets%20with%20citric%20acid%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%3C%2Ftr%3E%3C%2Ftbody%3E%3C%2Ftable%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20popped%20two%20of%20our%20go-to%20Lifesavers%20into%20the%20extractor%2C%20and%20when%20we%20fired%20up%20the%20machine%20again%2C%20it%20started%20producing%20cotton%20candy%20in%20seconds.%20Jolly%20Ranchers%20are%20another%20solid%20option%2C%20but%20they%20tend%20to%20come%20out%20with%20a%20less%20pleasant%20consistency.%20They%20aren't%20as%20light%20and%20fluffy%20as%20the%20Lifesavers%2C%20making%20for%20a%20less-perfect%20cotton%20candy%20cloud.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAround%20the%20holidays%2C%20we%20had%20a%20surplus%20of%20candy%20canes%2C%20which%20worked%20great%20in%20the%20cotton%20candy%20maker.%20Just%20be%20careful%20to%20break%20them%20up%2C%20and%20don't%20overfill%20the%20extractor.%20We%20found%20half%20a%20candy%20cane%20at%20a%20time%20worked%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221452%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20female-presenting%20person%20wearing%20a%20polka%20dot%20dress%20makes%20Ricola%20cotton%20candy%20using%20the%20Nostalgia%20Cotton%20Candy%20Machine.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65d8f5bcce7f1785b2e3922e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221089%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EEver%20since%20I%20learned%20I%20could%20make%20cotton%20candy%20using%20any%20hard%20candy%2C%20I've%20wanted%20to%20make%20cough%20drop%20cotton%20candy.%20This%20is%20my%20dream%20coming%20true.%3Cp%3EJames%20Brains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20weirdo%2C%20I%20simply%20had%20to%20try%20cough%20drops.%20I%20put%20two%20lozenges%20in%20the%20extractor%2C%20and%20believe%20it%20or%20not%2C%20I%20made%20cough-drop%20cotton%20candy.%20As%20a%20Ricola%20lover%2C%20I%20enjoyed%20it%2C%20but%20I'm%20unsure%20how%20practical%20it%20is.%20It%20may%20have%20been