d%20to%20produce%20a%20larger%20yield.%20Regardless%20of%20your%20sugar%20source%2C%20you%20can%20always%20stop%20the%20machine%20to%20add%20more%20and%20get%20a%20larger%20cotton%20candy%20cone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Cleanup%5C%22%3ECleanup%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221452%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Nostalgia%20Cotton%20Candy%20Maker%20is%20displayed%20with%20a%20candy%20ring%20around%20the%20outside.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65d8fadb6080194819f9dbfa%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221089%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20candy%20ring%20collects%20around%20the%20bowl%2C%20but%20it's%20easy%20to%20clean%20up%2C%20or%20if%20you're%20like%20me%2C%20you%20can%20eat%20it.%3Cp%3EJames%20Brains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ECleanup%20is%20a%20breeze.%20First%2C%20wait%20for%20the%20machine%20to%20cool%20down.%20Then%2C%20you%20can%20remove%20the%20bowl%20and%20wash%20it%20with%20mild%20detergent%20and%20water.%20I%20secretly%20enjoy%20eating%20some%20of%20the%20stuck-on%20candy%20before%20washing%20it.%20The%20reusable%20cones%20should%20also%20be%20washed%20by%20hand%2C%20though%20I've%20put%20them%20through%20the%20dishwasher's%20top%20rack%20and%20haven't%20had%20a%20problem.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Cons%20to%20consider%5C%22%3ECons%20to%20consider%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221452%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20person%20removes%20cotton%20candy%20from%20a%20cone%20into%20a%20Ziploc%20bag.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65d8fa126080194819f9db75%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221089%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EYou%20can%20make%20several%20matches%20of%20cotton%20candy%20at%20once%20and%20store%20them%20in%20a%20Ziploc%20bag%20for%20later%20enjoyment.%3Cp%3EJames%20Brains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20a%20learning%20curve%20to%20using%20the%20Nostalgia%20Hard%20Candy%20Cotton%20Candy%20Machine.%20You%20gotta%20get%20a%20feel%20for%20collecting%20the%20cotton%20candy%20threads%20with%20the%20cone%20and%20twisting%20it%20just%20right.%20My%20wife%20is%20a%20pro%20at%20it%2C%20and%20my%20kids%20have%20her%20make%20the%20cotton%20candy%20for%20them.%20A%20youngster%20could%20use%20the%20cotton%20candy%20maker%20but%20should%20have%20adult%20supervision.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Nostalgia%20maker%20is%20slower%20than%20the%20ones%20you%20might%20see%20at%20a%20fair%2C%20so%20be%20patient.%20My%20wife%20likes%20to%20make%20a%20lot%20at%20once%20and%20store%20it%20in%20a%20Ziploc%20bag%20for%20later%20snacking.%20We've%20found%20the%20cotton%20candy%20stores%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22The%20bottom%20line%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20bottom%20line%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221452%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20woman%20holds%20two%20cones%20of%20cotton%20candy%20while%20smiling%20at%20the%20camera.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65d8fbd090413ab8e1d68a13%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221089%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELook%20at%20how%20happy%20the%20cotton%20candy%20maker%20made%20my%20wife!%3Cp%3EJames%20Brains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOverall%2C%20this%20is%20the%20best%20present%20I've%20ever%20given%20my%20family.%20We've%20had%20the%20Nostalgia%20Cotton%20Candy%20Machine%20for%20two%20months%2C%20and%20they%20still%20love%20it.%20We%20have%20vegan%2C%20gluten-free%2C%20and%20just-plan-picky%20eaters%20in%20the%20house%2C%20and%20this%20is%20a%20treat%20we%20can%20all%20agree%20on.%20This%20machine%20will%20quickly%20pay%20for%20itself%20if%20you%20regularly%20spend%20money%20on%20cotton%20candy.%20Plus%2C%20it's%20regularly%20on%20sale%20for%20about%20%2450.%20If%20you%20want%20to%20be%20your%20