n%20units%20of%20electricity%20annually%20and%20offset%2035.5%20million%20metric%20tons%20of%20carbon%20dioxide%20emissions.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Business%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fbusiness%2Findia-business%2Fnlc-india-green-energy-signs-ppa-for-solar-power-project-with-guvnl%2Farticleshow%2F108276939.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fbusiness%2Findia-business%2Fnlc-india-green-energy-signs-ppa-for-solar-power-project-with-guvnl%2Famp_articleshow%2F108276939.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fbusiness%2Findia-business%2Fnlc-india-green-energy-signs-ppa-for-solar-power-project-with-guvnl%2Famp_articleshow%2F108276939.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22PM%20Modi's%20Rally%20In%20Srinagar%20Today%2C%20First%20Since%20Scrapping%20Of%20Article%20370%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20rally%20in%20Srinagar%20today%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20the%20biggest%20political%20rally%20in%20Kashmir%20since%20the%20scrapping%20of%20Article%20370%20five%20years%20ago.%20Thus%20would%20be%20his%20first%20rally%20in%20Kashmir%20since%202019.%20The%20arrangements%20indicate%20that%20the%20authorities%20are%20expecting%20such%20a%20huge%20crowd%20that%20Bakshi%20stadium%2C%20the%20venue%2C%20may%20not%20be%20large%20enough.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20preparations%20involve%20the%20biggest%20security%20exercise%20in%20recent%20times.%20Thousands%20of%20police%20and%20paramilitary%20personnel%20have%20been%20deployed%20across%20Srinagar.%20The%20areas%20around%20Bakshi%20stadium%20have%20turned%20into%20security%20fortress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20said%20more%20than%201%2C100%20buses%20have%20been%20pressed%20into%20service%20to%20transport%20people%20to%20the%20stadium.%20Around%20100%20buses%20have%20been%20requisitioned%20from%20a%20leading%20school%20in%20Srinagar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rally%20has%20a%20role%20in%20the%20BJP's%20larger%20narrative%20ahead%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%20The%20party%20has%20already%20made%20scrapping%20of%20Article%20370%20central%20to%20its%20election%20agenda%20by%20setting%20a%20target%20of%20370%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20claims%20two%20lakh%20people%20will%20be%20attending%20and%20the%20massive%20participation%20will%20be%20an%20endorsement%20of%20PM%20Modi's%20development%20agenda%20and%20scrapping%20of%20Article%20370.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20development%2C%20industrial%20growth.%20People%20are%20getting%20jobs.%20Ccorruption%20has%20ended%20in%20Kashmir.%20People%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20will%20be%20coming%20to%20listen%20to%20PM%20Modi%20for%20breaking%20the%20shackles%20of%20Article%20370.%20Two%20lakh%20people%20will%20attend%20the%20rally%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Tarun%20Chug%2C%20national%20general%20secretary%20of%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPeople%20from%20different%20districts%20from%20Jammu%20region%20and%20far%20off%20places%20in%20the%20Valley%20have%20already%20reached%20Srinagar.%20Massive%20arrangements%20have%20been%20made%20for%20their%20accommodation%20and%20food.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAntecedents%20of%20all%20participants%20have%20been%20verified%20by%20security%20agencies.%20Even%20journalists%20covering%20the%20rally%20had%20to%20undergo%20scrutiny%20and%20passes%20were%20issued%20only%20after%20security%20verifications.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETraffic%20advisory%20has%20been%20issued%20as%20several%20roads%20in%20Srinagar%20were%20closed%20for%20normal%20traffic.%20Many%20schools%20have%20been%20closed%20ahead%20of%20the%20Prime%20Minister's%20visit.%20Kashmir%20University%20has%20postponed%20all%20the%20exams%20scheduled%20for%20March%207%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20Bakshi%20stadium%20has%20an%20official%20seating%20capacity%20of%2020%2C000%2C%20more%20people%20can%20be%20accommodated%20on%20the%20ground.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThousands%20of%20government%20employees%20have%20been%20asked%20to%20attend%20and%20arrangements%20have%20been%20made%20to%20get%20them%20to%20the%20venue.%20A%20large%20number%20of%20self-help%20groups%20have%20also%20been%20roped%20in%20to%20join%20the%20mega%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBig%20screens%20are%20being%20installed%20in%20various%20districts%20to%20live%20stream%20the%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20is%20expected%20to%20announce%20several%20projects%20related%20to%20tourism%20and%20agriculture.%20He%20would%20also%20inaugurate%20an%20integrated%20development%20project%20for%20Kashmir's%20revered%20Hazratbal%20Shrine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20PM%20Modi's%20second%20visit%20to%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20in%20less%20than%20three%20weeks.%20On%20February%2020%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20addressed%20a%20rally%20in%20Jammu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi's%20rally%20is%20seen%20as%20an%20attempt%20by%20the%20BJP%20to%20gain%20foothold%20in%20Kashmir%20Valley%2C%20where%20it%20has%20never%20won%20a%20seat%20for%20assembly%20or%20parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20party%20is%20hoping%20that%20inclusion%20of%20the%20pahari%20community%20in%20the%20Scheduled%20Tribe%20list%20may%20help%20them%20to%20strengthen%20foothold%20in%20the%20Valley%20and%20Muslim-dominated%20regions%20of%20Jammu.%20Several%20pahari%20leaders%20have%20already%20joined%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709751780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fp2gt8pf_kashmir-generic_625x300_10_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-modis-rally-in-srinagar-tomorrow-first-since-scrapping-of-article-370-5189985%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20rally%20in%20Srinagar%20today%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20the%20biggest%20political%20rally%20in%20Kashmir%20since%20the%20scrapping%20of%20Article%20370%20five%20y