rc%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F06235340%2FIndia-and-US-n-A-2.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%3Cstrong%3EDelhi%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20United%20States%20and%20India%20on%20Wednesday%20(March%206)%20reiterated%20the%20call%20for%20justice%20for%20the%20masterminds%20of%20the%2026%2F11%20Mumbai%20and%20Pathankot%20Air%20Force%20Base%20terror%20attacks.%20However%2C%20both%20countries%20maintained%20public%20silence%20regarding%20any%20discussion%20of%20the%20allegations%20of%20a%20conspiracy%20to%20assassinate%20a%20Sikh%20American-Canadian%20lawyer.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%20senior%20officials%20from%20India%20and%20the%20United%20States%20took%20part%20in%20a%20meeting%20of%20the%20Counterterrorism%20Joint%20Working%20Group%20and%20Designations%20Dialogue%20at%20Washington.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mea.gov.in%2Fbilateral-documents.htm%3Fdtl%2F37682%2FJoint_Statement_of_the_20th_US_India_Counterterrorism_Joint_Working_Group_CTJWG_and_6th_Designations_Dialogue%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20joint%20statement%20issued%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20after%20the%20meeting%20stated%20that%20both%20countries%20%E2%80%9Ccalled%20for%20the%20perpetrators%20of%20the%2026%2F11%20Mumbai%20and%20Pathankot%20terrorist%20attacks%20to%20be%20brought%20to%20justice%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20also%20called%20for%20concerted%20action%20against%20all%20terrorist%20groups%2C%20including%20groups%20proscribed%20by%20the%20United%20Nations%20Security%20Council%20(UNSC)%201267%20Sanctions%20Committee%2C%20such%20as%20al-Qaida%2C%20ISIS%2FDaesh%2C%20Lashkar-e-Tayyiba%20(LeT)%2C%20and%20Jaish-e-Mohammad%20(JeM)%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAdditionally%2C%20the%20statement%20mentioned%20that%20both%20sides%20%E2%80%9Cexchanged%20information%20regarding%20priorities%20and%20procedures%20for%20designating%20various%20terrorist%20entities%2Fgroups%20and%20individuals%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%20and%20the%20United%20States%20have%20jointly%20submitted%20proposals%20to%20a%20UN%20Security%20Council%20committee%20for%20listing%20several%20Pakistan-based%20terrorists%20in%20the%20council%E2%80%99s%20sanctions%20list.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20most%20of%20them%20were%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fchina-unsc-sanction-lashkar-e-taiba-shahid-mahmood%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eblocked%20by%20China%20in%20recent%20years%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20meeting%20also%20took%20place%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20US%20prosecutors%20accusing%20an%20unnamed%20Indian%20official%20for%20being%20the%20main%20mastermind%20in%20the%20foiled%20attempt%20to%20target%20Gurpatwant%20Singh%20Pannun%2C%20the%20general%20counsel%20for%20a%20proscribed%20group%20named%20Sikhs%20for%20Justice.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20unsealed%20US%20indictment%20had%20also%20linked%20the%20conspiracy%20to%20the%20killing%20of%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar%20in%20Canada%20last%20year.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%20had%20set%20up%20a%20high-level%20committee%20to%20probe%20the%20US%20allegations%2C%20but%20there%20has%20been%20no%20public%20confirmation%20whether%20the%20investigation%20has%20been%20completed%20or%20is%20still%20ongoing.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20joint%20statement%20did%20not%20mention%20whether%20the%20issue%20was%20brought%20up%20and%20there%20have%20been%20no%20additional%20remarks%20from%20either%20side%20on%20this%20matter.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709749488000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F06235340%2FIndia-and-US-n-A-2.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fus-and-india-reiterate-call-for-justice-on-terror-attacks-silent-on-pannun-allegations%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Indian%20and%20US%20officials%20in%20Washington%20also%20called%20for%20%E2%80%9Cconcerted%20action%20against%20all%20terrorist%20groups%E2%80%9D%2C%20including%20those%20proscribed%20by%20the%20United%20Nations%20Security%20Council%20sanctions%20committee%2C%20such%20as%20al-Qaida%2C%20ISIS%2C%20Lashkar-e-Tayyiba%20and%20Jaish-e-Mohammad.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fus-and-india-reiterate-call-for-justice-on-terror-attacks-silent-on-pannun-allegations%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Former%20world%20chess%20champion%20Kasparov%20added%20to%20Russian%20'terrorists%20and%20extremists'%20list%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709749301000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108276643%2Cimgsize-1197203.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fformer-world-chess-champion-kasparov-added-to-russian-terrorists-and-extremists-list%2Farticleshow%2F108276615.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F108276615.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3E%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20World%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fformer-world-chess-champion-kasparov-added-to-russian-terrorists-and-extremists-list%2Farticleshow%2F108276615.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fformer-world-chess-champion-kasparov-added-to-russian-terrorists-and-extremists-list%2Famp_articleshow%2F108276615.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fformer-world-chess-champion-kasparov-added-to-russian-terrorists-and-extremists-list%2Famp_articleshow%2F108276615.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Union%20Minister's%20Big%20Charge%20On%20'Those%20Not%20Giving%20Peace%20A%20Chance'%20In%20Manipur%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EUnion%20Minister%20Rajkumar%20Ranjan%20Singh%20has%20asked%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20to%20set%20up%20a%20system%20that%20can%20bring%20credible%20civil%20society%20groups%20from%20both%20the%20Kuki-Zo%20tribes%20and%20the%20Meitei%20community%20for%20sincere%20talks%20to%20solve%20the%20Manipur%20crisis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWithout%20naming%20anyone%2C%20Mr%20Singh%20in%20a%20letter%20to%20PM%20Modi%20alleged%20Manipur%20is%20not%20being%20allowed%20to%20live%20in%20peace%20and%20return%20to%20normalcy%20by%20%26quot%3Bsome%20few%20political%20leaders%2C%20a%20handful%20of%20armed%20groups%2C%20and%20wrongly%20motivated%20scoundrels.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Minister%20of%20State%20for%20External%20Affairs%20and%20Education%20in%20the%20letter%20requested%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20to%20ensure%20civil%20society%20organisations%20(CSOs)%20from%20both%20sides%20%26quot%3Bare%20not%20coerced%20or%20influenced%20by%20armed%20militias%20and%20insurgents.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BConsidering%20the%20fluid%20law%20and%20order%20situation%20due%20to%20the%20ethnic%20strife%20and%20tension%2C%20we%20may%20seriously%20start%20a%20people-to-people%20contact%20movement%20via%20CSOs%20of%20the%20Meiteis%20and%20the%20Kukis%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Singh%2C%20who%20represents%20the%20Inner%20Manipur%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%2C%20said%20in%20the%20letter%20to%20PM%20Modi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPMO%20(Prime%20Minister's%20Office)%20may%20find%20some%20credible%20CSOs%20like%20the%20time-tested%20'Manipur%20Cultural%20Integration%20Conference'%20on%20both%20sides%20and%20ask%20them%20to%20start%20negotiations%20for%20a%20practical%2C%20amicable%20solution%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Union%20Minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOnly%20people-to-people%20communication%20and%20understanding%20will%20show%20us%20the%20path%20for%20resolving%20the%20issues.%20Arms%20and%20bullets%20can't%20bring%20about%20a%20solution.%20Violence%20begets%20violence.%20So%20let%20the%20peace-loving%20citizens%20start%20the%20negotiation%20at%20the%20ground%20level%20under%20the%20PMO's%20patronage%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Singh%20said%20in%20the%20two-page%20letter.%20NDTV%20has%20seen%20a%20copy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Centre%20must%20ensure%20that%20they%20are%20not%20coerced%20or%20influenced%20by%20the%20armed%20militias%20or%20insurgents%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added%2C%20alluding%20to%20the%20huge%20number%20of%20armed%20groups%20and%20people%20in%20Manipur%20who%20call%20themselves%20%26quot%3Bvillage%20defence%20volunteers%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fq90j60ng_manipur-generic_625x300_05_March_24.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20number%20of%20looted%20guns%20in%20circulation%20in%20Manipur%20is%20in%20thousands.%20The%20Manipur%20Police%20have%20said%20the%20Meitei%20youth%20organisation%20Arambai%20Teggol%20has%20been%20taking%20advantage%20of%20the%20crisis%20to%20further%20their%20own%20agenda.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20hill%20areas%2C%20the%2025-odd%20Kuki-Zo%20insurgent%20groups%20that%20have%20signed%20the%20tripartite%20suspension%20of%20operations%20(SoO)%20agreement%20with%20the%20Centre%20and%20the%20state%20government%20have%20been%20accused%20of%20murdering%20civilians%2C%20highway%20extortion%2C%20and%20drug%20smuggling%20by%20using%20the%20safety%20net%20provided%20by%20the%20SoO%20agreement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20honest%20reading%20is%20that%20common%20people%20desperately%20want%20restoration%20of%20peace%20and%20normalcy%20in%20Manipur.%20Some%20few%20political%20leaders%2C%20a%20handful%20of%20armed%20groups%2C%20and%20wrongly%20motivated%20scoundrels%20are%20not%20allowing%20it%20to%20happen...%20A%20strong%20intervention%20shall%20make%20both%20sides%20fall%20in%20line%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Singh%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Union%20Minister%20also%20highlighted%20the%20need%20for%20posting%20the%20Border%20Security%20Force%20(BSF)%20along%20the%20India-Myanmar%20border.%20Telling%20from%20his%20experience%2C%20Mr%20Singh%20said%20the%20BSF%20is%20very%20effective%20in%20keeping%20borders%20safe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%2070s%20(i.e.%2050%20years%20ago)%20as%20a%20young%20researcher%2C%20I%20did%20a%20lot%20of%20travelling%20along%20the%20Indo-Myanmar%20border%20for%20research%20and%20in%20personal%20interest.%20During%20those%20days%20the%20BSF%20was%20guarding%20the%20border%20and%20in%20every%2020-30%20km%2C%20there%20was%20a%20BSF%20post%20along%20the%20international%20boundary.%20We%20found%20them%20taking%20patrol%20to%20and%20fro%20along%20the%20border%20in%20the%20difficult%20hilly-forest%20terrain%2C%20even%20though%20there%20was%20no%20proper%20path%20or%20way%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Singh%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBecause%20of%20their%20strict%20vigil%2C%20there%20was%20hardly%20any%20intrusion%20or%20smuggling...%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20widely%20cited%20issues%20in%20current%20day%20Manipur%20such%20as%20drugs%20smuggling%20and%20illegal%20immigration%2C%20which%20are%20seen%20as%20some%20factors%20behind%20the%20Manipur%20crisis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fvkl1bcig_churachandpur_625x300_23_September_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Union%20Minister's%20comments%20also%20come%20days%20after%20Manipur%20Chief%20Minister%20N%20Biren%20Singh%20said%20BSF%20soldiers%20have%20started%20deployment%20along%20the%20border%20with%20Myanmar.%20The%20Assam%20Rifles%2C%20whose%20operational%20control%20is%20with%20the%20army%20and%20administrative%20control%20with%20the%20Home%20Ministry%2C%20has%20so%20far%20been%20shouldering%20the%20dual%20roles%20of%20guarding%20the%20border%20and%20running%20counter-insurgency%20operations%20at%20the%20same%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ethnic%20violence%20in%20Manipur%20over%20disagreements%20on%20land%2C%20resources%2C%20political%20representation%2C%20and%20affirmative%20action%20policies%20has%20dragged%20on%20for%2010%20months%20now.%20Over%20180%20have%20died%20and%20thousands%20have%20been%20internally%20displaced.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709749200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-05%2Fkad751cg_rk-ranjan_625x300_21_May_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Funion-minister-rajkumar-ranjan-singh-big-charge-on-those-not-giving-peace-a-chance-in-manipur-5189754%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Union%20Minister%20Rajkumar%20Ranjan%20Singh%20has%20asked%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20to%20set%20up%20a%20system%20that%20can%20bring%20credible%20civil%20society%20groups%20from%20both%20the%20Kuki-Zo%20tribes%20and%20the%20Meitei%20community%20for%20sincere%20talks%20to%20solve%20the%20Manipur%20crisis.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Funion-minister-rajkumar-ranjan-singh-big-charge-on-those-not-giving-peace-a-chance-in-manipur-5189754%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Funion-minister-rajkumar-ranjan-singh-big-charge-on-those-not-giving-peace-a-chance-in-manipur-5189754%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Funion-minister-rajkumar-ranjan-singh-big-charge-on-those-not-giving-peace-a-chance-in-manipur-5189754%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22INDIA%20Bloc%20Attempts%20Coup%20In%20Bihar%2C%20Makes%208-Seat%20Offer%20To%20BJP%20Ally%3A%20Sources%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20seat-sharing%20tussle%20within%20the%20NDA%20over%20Bihar%20continues%2C%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20has%20made%20a%20move%20on%20the%20political%20chessboard%20and%20offered%20eight%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20the%20state%20and%20two%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20to%20Lok%20Janshakti%20Party%20(Ram%20Vilas)%20chief%20Chirag%20Paswan%2C%20sources%20have%20told%20NDTV.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20proposal%20may%20prove%20to%20be%20tempting%20to%20Mr%20Paswan%2C%20who%20is%20reportedly%20being%20offered%20only%20six%20Lok%20Sabha%20constituencies%20in%20Bihar%20by%20the%20NDA%20and%20even%20those%20come%20with%20a%20caveat%20-%20the%20seats%20will%20have%20to%20be%20split%20with%20his%20uncle%20and%20Rashtriya%20Lok%20Janshakti%20Party%20chief%20Pashupati%20Paras%2C%20who%20he%20is%20not%20on%20the%20best%20terms%20with.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20INDIA%20alliance%20offer%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20includes%20all%20six%20seats%20that%20the%20undivided%20Lok%20Janshakti%20Party%20(LJP)%20had%20contested%20in%202019%2C%20and%20a%20deal%20sweetener%20in%20the%20form%20of%20two%20additional%20constituencies%20in%20Bihar%20and%20two%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20the%20sources%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Lok%20Janshakti%20Party%20had%20split%20in%202021%2C%20following%20a%20coup%20by%20Mr%20Paras%20a%20year%20after%20the%20death%20of%20party%20chief%20and%20veteran%20leader%20Ram%20Vilas%20Paswan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Paswan%20was%20the%20brother%20of%20Mr%20Paras%20and%20father%20of%20Chirag%20Paswan.%20After%20Mr%20Paras%20was%20given%20a%20cabinet%20berth%20by%20the%20BJP-led%20NDA%2C%20Chirag%20Paswan%20had%20attacked%20the%20Janata%20Dal%20United%20and%20Bihar%20Chief%20Minister%20Nitish%20Kumar.%20He%20had%2C%20however%2C%20refrained%20from%20targeting%20the%20BJP%20and%20PM%20Narendra%20Modi%20-%20whom%20he%20had%20earlier%20called%20his%20Ram%20and%20said%20he%20was%20his%20Hanuman.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaving%20quit%20the%20NDA%20in%202020%20over%20differences%20with%20Mr%20Kumar%2C%20Chirag%20Paswan%20had%20rejoined%20the%20alliance%20last%20year%2C%20when%20the%20Bihar%20chief%20minister%20was%20a%20part%20of%20the%20Mahagathbandhan%2C%20which%20includes%20the%20Lalu%20Yadav-led%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%20and%20the%20Congress.%20Tensions%20have%20reportedly%20been%20bubbling%20under%20the%20surface%20ever%20since%20the%20JDU%20chief%20returned%20to%20the%20NDA%20earlier%20this%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20also%20differences%20between%20Mr%20Paswan%20and%20Mr%20Paras%20over%20the%20latter's%20Hajipur%20Lok%20Sabha%20constituency.%20While%20Mr%20Paras%20is%20the%20sitting%20MP%20from%20the%20seat%2C%20Mr%20Paswan%20has%20sought%20to%20stake%20claim%20to%20it%20because%20it%20was%20his%20late%20father's%20former%20constituency%20and%20his%20%3Cem%3E%26quot%3Bkarmabhoomi%26quot%3B%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESeat%20Division%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20and%20the%20JDU%20had%20fought%2017%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20each%20in%20Bihar%20in%202019%20and%20the%20six%20remaining%20constituencies%20had%20been%20contested%20by%20the%20LJP.%20The%20BJP%20and%20the%20LJP%20had%20won%20all%20the%20seats%20they%20had%20contested%20and%20the%20JDU%20had%20fallen%20short%20only%20in%20Kishanganj%2C%20which%20it%20had%20lost%20to%20the%20Congress.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bigger%20partners%20in%20the%20NDA%20are%20reportedly%20keen%20on%20repeating%20the%20same%20arrangement%2C%20leaving%20Mr%20Paras%20and%20Mr%20Paswan's%20party%20to%20work%20out%20an%20understanding%20over%20the%20six%20seats%20the%20LJP%20had%20contested%20the%20last%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20Bihar%20Mahagathbandhan%2C%20however%2C%2017%20seats%20-%20which%20would%20have%20otherwise%20gone%20to%20the%20JDU%20-%20have%20been%20opened%20up.%20This%20has%20left%20them%20the%20room%20to%20manoeuvre%20and%20try%20and%20rope%20in%20Mr%20Paswan's%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20move%20does%20work%20out%2C%20it%20will%20be%20a%20boost%20to%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%2C%20which%20has%20faced%20trouble%20in%20finalising%20seat-sharing%20in%20several%20states%2C%20including%20West%20Bengal%20and%20Punjab.%20Bihar%2C%20with%20its%2040%20seats%2C%20sends%20the%20fourth-highest%20number%20of%20MPs%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20is%20fancying%20its%20chances%20of%20giving%20pause%20to%20the%20NDA%20juggernaut%20after%20the%2039-1%20rout%20it%20had%20faced%20its%20chances.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20blow%20to%20the%20NDA%20and%20the%20JDU%20could%20also%20act%20as%20a%20salve%20for%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%2C%20which%20is%20still%20smarting%20from%20Mr%20Kumar's%20fresh%20volte-face%20in%20January.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709749080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2F7oepsuc8_chirag-paswan-jp-nadda-ndtv_650x400_17_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchirag-paswan-nda-lok-sabha-election-2024-india-bloc-attempts-coup-in-bihar-makes-8-seat-offer-to-bjp-ally-sources-5189745%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20the%20seat-sharing%20tussle%20within%20the%20NDA%20over%20Bihar%20continues%2C%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20has%20offered%20eight%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20the%20state%20and%20two%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20to%20Lok%20Janshakti%20Party%20(Ram%20Vilas)%20chief%20Chirag%20Paswan%2C%20sources%20have%20told%20NDTV.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchirag-paswan-nda-lok-sabha-election-2024-india-bloc-attempts-coup-in-bihar-makes-8-seat-offer-to-bjp-ally-sources-5189745%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchirag-paswan-nda-lok-sabha-election-2024-india-bloc-attempts-coup-in-bihar-makes-8-seat-offer-to-bjp-ally-sources-5189745%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchirag-paswan-nda-lok-sabha-election-2024-india-bloc-attempts-coup-in-bihar-makes-8-seat-offer-to-bjp-ally-sources-5189745%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Glenn%20Saldanha%20announced%20resignation%20as%20chairman%20of%20Glenmark%20Life%20Sciences%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709749014000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2018-11%2F20%2Ffull%2F1542728820-8123.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fglenn-saldanha-announced-resignation-as-chairman-of-glenmark-life-sciences-124030600944_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Glenmark%20Life%20Sciences%20Ltd%20on%20Wednesday%20said%20its%20Chairman%20Glenn%20Saldanha%20and%20non-executive%20director%20VS%20Mani%20have%20resigned%20following%20change%20in%20ownership%20of%20the%20company%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fglenn-saldanha-announced-resignation-as-chairman-of-glenmark-life-sciences-124030600944_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fglenn-saldanha-announced-resignation-as-chairman-of-glenmark-life-sciences-124030600944_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fglenn-saldanha-announced-resignation-as-chairman-of-glenmark-life-sciences-124030600944_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Husband%20Expecting%20Wife%20To%20Do%20Household%20Chores%20Is%20Not%20Cruelty%3A%20Delhi%20High%20Court%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAsking%20a%20husband%20to%20live%20separately%20from%20his%20family%20amounts%20to%20cruelty%20by%20his%20wife%2C%20the%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20has%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20also%20stated%20that%20in%20a%20marriage%2C%20the%20intent%20is%20to%20share%20the%20responsibilities%20of%20a%20future%20life%20and%20the%20husband%20expecting%20his%20wife%20to%20do%20household%20chores%20cannot%20be%20termed%20as%20cruelty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsking%20a%20married%20woman%20to%20do%20household%20work%20cannot%20be%20equated%20to%20the%20work%20of%20a%20help%20as%20it%20shall%20be%20counted%20as%20her%20love%20and%20affection%20for%20her%20family%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court's%20observations%20came%20while%20dealing%20with%20an%20appeal%20by%20a%20man%20against%20a%20family%20court%20order%20refusing%20to%20dissolve%20his%20marriage%20on%20the%20ground%20of%20cruelty%20by%20his%20wife.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20appellant%20husband%2C%20a%20CISF%20member%2C%20said%20he%20was%20aggrieved%20by%20the%20respondent%20wife's%20non-contribution%20in%20household%20chores%2C%20abandonment%20of%20matrimonial%20home%20and%20false%20implication%20in%20criminal%20cases%20at%20her%20behest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20alleged%20that%20the%20respondent%20and%20her%20family%20insisted%20that%20he%20lived%20separately%20from%20his%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20bench%20headed%20by%20Justice%20Suresh%20Kumar%20Kait%20said%20that%20a%20son%20has%20a%20moral%20and%20legal%20obligation%20to%20take%20care%20of%20his%20aged%20parents%20who%20have%20no%20or%20negligible%20source%20of%20income%2C%20and%20it%20is%20not%20a%20desirable%20culture%20for%20Hindu%20son%20to%20get%20separated%20from%20his%20family%20after%20marriage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20case%20of%20Narendra%20vs%20K.%20Meena%2C%20it%20has%20been%20observed%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20that%20asking%20a%20son%20to%20separate%20from%20his%20family%20amount%20to%20cruelty.%20It%20was%20stated%20that%2C%20for%20a%20Hindu%20son%20in%20India%2C%20it%20is%20not%20a%20common%20practice%20or%20desirable%20culture%20to%20get%20separated%20from%20his%20family%20after%20marriage%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%2C%20also%20comprising%20Justice%20Neena%20Bansal%20Krishna%2C%20said%20in%20a%20recent%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20the%20parties%20enter%20into%20a%20wedlock%2C%20their%20intent%20is%20to%20share%20the%20responsibilities%20of%20future%20life.%20In%20a%20catena%20of%20decisions%2C%20it%20has%20already%20been%20held%20that%20if%20a%20married%20woman%20is%20asked%20to%20do%20household%20work%2C%20the%20same%20cannot%20be%20equated%20to%20the%20work%20of%20a%20maid%20servant%20and%20shall%20be%20counted%20as%20her%20love%20and%20affection%20for%20her%20family.%20In%20certain%20strata%2C%20the%20husband%20takes%20over%20the%20financial%20obligations%20and%20wife%20accepts%20household%20responsibility.%20Such%20is%20the%20present%20case.%20Even%20if%20appellant%20expected%20the%20respondent%20to%20do%20household%20chores%2C%20it%20cannot%20be%20termed%20as%20cruelty%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20observed%20that%20in%20the%20present%20case%2C%20the%20appellant%20bowed%20to%20the%20desires%20of%20respondent%20and%20arranged%20for%20a%20separate%20accommodation%20to%20save%20his%20matrimonial%20life%20but%20she%20abandoned%20the%20matrimonial%20home%20and%20lived%20with%20her%20parents%20on%20one%20pretext%20or%20another.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%20one%20hand%20respondent%20denied%20to%20live%20with%20her%20in-laws%20and%20over%20it%2C%20she%20chose%20to%20frequently%20live%20with%20her%20parents.%20To%20nurture%20the%20matrimonial%20bond%2C%20it%20is%20of%20high%20significance%20that%20parties%20live%20together%20and%20avoid%20leaving%20each%20other's%20company%20frequently.%20Temporary%20separation%20gives%20a%20sense%20of%20insecurity%20in%20the%20mind%20of%20a%20spouse%20that%20the%20other%20is%20not%20willing%20to%20continue%20the%20matrimonial%20bond%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20observed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20also%20said%20while%20filing%20of%20a%20criminal%20complaint%20per-se%20does%20not%20amount%20to%20cruelty%2C%20grave%20and%20uncorroborated%20allegations%20amount%20to%20cruelty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20noted%20that%20the%20couple%20had%20been%20living%20separately%20since%202010%20and%20the%20respondent%20had%20%26quot%3Bno%20intention%20to%20live%20in%20joint%20family%20and%20to%20make%20herself%20comfortable%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20appellant%20on%20the%20other%20hand%20by%20arranging%20separate%20accommodation%20tried%20his%20best%20to%20keep%20her%20happy%2C%20however%2C%20by%20choosing%20to%20stay%20with%20her%20parents%2C%20she%20has%20not%20only%20ignored%20her%20matrimonial%20obligations%20but%20also%20deprived%20the%20appellant%20of%20his%20fatherhood%20by%20keeping%20him%20away%20from%20his%20son%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20court%20is%20of%20the%20considered%20opinion%20that%20appellant%20has%20been%20subjected%20to%20cruelty%20at%20the%20hands%20of%20respondent-wife.%20The%20impugned%20judgment%20dated%2025.11.2019%20is%20hereby%20set%20aside%20and%20the%20appellant%20is%20granted%20divorce%20under%20Section%2013(1)%20(ia)%20of%20the%20Hindu%20Marriage%20Act%2C%201955%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20ordered.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709748960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2015-12%2Fcourt-generic-650x400_650x400_81450530482.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-high-court-husband-expecting-wife-to-do-household-chores-is-not-cruelty-5188757%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Asking%20a%20husban