pan%3EThe%20women%20conveyed%20their%20grievances%2C%20including%20allegations%20of%20sexual%20assault%2C%20mental%20torture%2C%20wage%20confiscation%20and%20physical%20abuse.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESpeaking%20to%20the%20media%20after%20the%20interaction%2C%20a%20woman%20stated%20that%20they%20had%20specifically%20requested%20for%20the%20deployment%20of%20security%20forces%20controlled%20by%20the%20Union%20government%20in%20the%20island%2C%20citing%20collusion%20between%20local%20Trinamool%20Congress%20leaders%20and%20the%20police.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENotably%2C%20no%20other%20BJP%20leader%20was%20permitted%20to%20participate%20in%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20discussion%20with%20the%20women.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20BJP%20asserted%20that%20the%20prime%20minister%20had%20assured%20the%20women%20of%20addressing%20their%20concerns.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAddressing%20the%20crowd%20during%20the%20rally%2C%20Modi%20again%20raised%20the%20Sandeshkhali%20issue%20and%20declared%20that%20the%20impact%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9CSandeshkhali%20storm%E2%80%9D%20has%20to%20reach%20every%20part%20of%20Bengal.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFocusing%20on%20the%20women%E2%80%99s%20vote%20%E2%80%93%20women%20are%20a%20key%20vote%20bloc%20of%20Trinamool%20leader%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20%E2%80%93%20Modi%20talked%20about%20%E2%80%98nari%20shakti%E2%80%99%20(woman%20power)%20and%20asserted%20that%20it%20has%20the%20power%20to%20topple%20the%20Trinamool%20government%20in%20the%20state.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EModi%20also%20termed%20the%20events%20involving%20women%20in%20Sandeshkhali%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Cmatter%20of%20shame%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EReacting%20to%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20address%2C%20Trinamool%20spokesperson%20and%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20Derek%20O%E2%80%99Brien%20spoke%20about%20inaction%20against%20the%20BJP%20MP%20and%20former%20Wres