%20change%20the%20venue%20twice%20and%20yet%20there%20was%20not%20an%20inch%20of%20space%20left%20to%20accommodate%20more%20people%20in%20the%20biggest%20space%20available%20at%20LSE.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20pivotal%20role%20of%20publishing%20houses%20in%20commissioning%20and%20supporting%20the%20interpretation%20of%20shifting%20realities%20cannot%20be%20overstated.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EJaffrelot%E2%80%99s%20initial%20manuscript%2C%20poised%20for%20release%20in%202013%2C%20ahead%20of%20the%202014%20general%20election%2C%20was%20held%20back%20due%20to%20necessary%20revisions.%20A%20decade%20later%2C%20revisiting%20the%20manuscript%20under%20the%20auspices%20of%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hurstpublishers.com%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EHurst%20Publication%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0allowed%20for%20deeper%20contemplation%2C%20unravelling%20myriad%20transformations.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20publication%20house%20has%20become%20instrumental%20in%20publishing%20a%20range%20of%20interesting%20and%20timely%20books%20in%20a%20mammoth%20year%20of%20elections%20across%20the%20democratic%20world.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EFour%20pillars%20of%20Narendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Gujarat%20Model%E2%80%99%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EJaffrelot%20calls%20for%20urgent%20attention%20to%20the%20%E2%80%98Gujarat%20Model%E2%80%99%20that%20relied%20on%20four%20pillars%3A%20%E2%80%9Ccommunal%20polarisation%20resulting%20in%20Hindu%20majoritarianism%3B%20the%20politicisation%20of%20state%20institutions%2C%20including%20the%20police%20and%20the%20judiciary%3B%20a%20political%20economy%20implying%20crony%20capitalism%20and%20growing%20inequalities%20and%20populist%20techniques%20of%20communication%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20passionately%20argues%20in%20the%20book%20that%20the%20divisive%20polarisation%20technique%20was%20developed%20in%20Gujarat%2C%20which%20was%20later%20used%20nationally%20%E2%80%93%20changing%20the%20length%20and%20breadth%20of%20the%20values%20India%20ever%20stood%20for.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FsGRQOR0P4c8%3Fsi%3DkG96Mr0KdzG_IZ3q%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CCommunal%20riot%20was%20a%20recipe%20for%20the%20electoral%20success%20of%20the%20BJP%2C%20and%20that%20was%20demonstrated%20in%20the%202002%20elections%2C%20when%20the%20BJP%20won%20those%20seats%20where%20riots%20occurred%E2%80%9D%2C%20he%20concludes%20based%20on%20his%20research%20on%20different%20constituencies%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20research%20shows%20that%20the%20communal%20polarisation%20technique%20has%20helped%20Modi%20sustain%20the%20power%20in%202002%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20importantly%2C%20it%20is%20noteworthy%20that%20the%20polarisation%20went%20beyond%20the%20pogrom.%20Between%202003%20and%202006%2C%20the%20BJP%20continued%20to%20polarise%20the%20politics%20of%20fear%20under%20the%20aegis%20of%20fake%20encounters%2C%20which%20today%20seems%20to%20be%20a%20norm%20in%20New%20India%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20how%20did%20the%20%E2%80%98deinstitutionalisation%20of%20the%20rule%20of%20law%E2%80%99%20play%20out%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20started%20with%20the%20police%3B%20the%20promotion%20of%20Mr%20%5BD.G.%5D%20Vanzara%20and%20many%20other%20officers%20fits%20into%20the%20transformation%20of%20the%20police%20into%20the%20instrument%20of%20political%20agenda.%20Similar%20occurrences%20are%20visible%20in%20today%E2%80%99s%20India%2C%20where%20the%20rule%20of%20law%20was%20undermined%20and%20the%20rule%20of%20vigilantism%20was%20highlighted%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%20%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Fnarendra-modi-a-pracharak-morphed-into-a-politician%5C%22%3ENarendra%20Modi%3A%20A%20Pracharak%20Morphed%20into%20a%20Politician%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3E%E2%80%98Institutional%20ramifications%E2%80%99%20under%20Modi%20as%20CM%20and%20PM%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECommenting%20on%20the%20important%20role%20the%20book%20plays%20through%20its%20%E2%80%9Ccomprehensive%20approach%20and%20meticulous%20details%E2%80%9D%2C%20Sheba%20Tejani%2C%20a%20lecturer%20in%20international%20development%20at%20King%E2%80%99s%20College%20London%2C%20said%20that%20the%20book%20%E2%80%9Cturns%20into%20our%20attention%20to%20various%20dimensions%20of%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20rule%20in%20Gujarat%2C%20from%20the%20political%2C%20institutional%2C%20social%20and%20economic%20aspects.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShe%20continued%3A%20%E2%80%9CIt%20documents%20not%20only%20the%20major%20events%2C%20trends%20and%20transformations%20in%20Gujarat%20from%20the%202000s%2C%20but%20as%20importantly%20analyses%20techniques%2C%20discourses%20and%20politics%20that%20capitalised%20the%20shifts.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20book%20further%20illuminates%20the%20interlinkages%20between%20various%20moralities%20of%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20rule%20to%20cast%20light%20on%20the%20tapestry%20of%20Hindu%20nationalism%20that%20has%20been%20grown%20in%20Gujarat.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERecapitulating%20the%20three%20important%20lessons%20based%20on%20the%20book%2C%20Pavithra%20Suryanarayan%2C%20assistant%20professor%20in%20the%20department%20of%20government%20at%20LSE%2C%20said%20that%20this%20is%20not%20only%20the%20story%20of%20the%20rise%20of%20Modi%20but%20the%20%E2%80%9Cinstitutional%20consequences%20of%20the%20rise%20of%20Modi%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShe%20argues%20that%20the%20book%20discusses%20%E2%80%9Chow%20Modi%20managed%20all%20of%20this%20between%20the%20economic%20and%20electoral%20bases%20of%20support%2C%20both%20developing%20a%20specific%20form%20of%20capitalism%20and%20a%20specific%20language%20of%20populism.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EImportantly%2C%20Suryanarayan%20positions%20the%20book%20in%20a%20different%20category.%20She%20highlighted%20that%20very%20little%20has%20been%20written%20on%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20institutional%20ramifications%20of%20the%20kind%20of%20rule%20Modi%20brought%20in%20Gujarat%20as%20a%20CM%20and%20now%20as%20PM%E2%80%9D%20and%20in%20her%20opinion%2C%20this%20book%20has%20successfully%20examined%20this.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fas-the-gujarat-model-goes-national-hindutva-hunts-for-the-enemy-in-our-midst%5C%22%3EAs%20the%20Gujarat%20Model%20Goes%20National%2C%20Hindutva%20Hunts%20for%20the%20%E2%80%98Enemy%20in%20Our%20Midst%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3E%E2%80%98Model%20of%20surveillance%E2%80%99%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EJaffrelot%20briefly%20discussed%20the%20role%20of%20surveillance%20while%20talking%20about%20the%20role%20of%20vigilantism.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20kind%20of%20surveillance%20we%20see%20today%20in%20India%20was%20invented%20in%20Gujarat%2020%20years%20ago.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20this%20book%2C%20the%20author%20inquires%20into%20the%20%E2%80%9Cassociation%20between%20the%20Modi%20government%20and%20rising%20stars%20of%20Indian%20capitalism%E2%80%9D.%20He%20also%20talked%20about%20the%20%E2%80%98Vibrant%20Gujarat%20summit%E2%80%99%20and%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20promoted%20the%20big%20companies%20at%20the%20expense%20of%20MSMEs%20%5Bmicro%2C%20small%20and%20medium%20enterprises%5D%2C%20entrepreneurship%20and%20co-operatives.%20This%20particular%20economy%20is%20making%20the%20society%20of%20Gujarat%20more%20unequal%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CHuman%20development%20such%20as%20health%20and%20education%20were%20not%20in%20the%20priority%20list%20of%20the%20Modi%20government%2C%20the%20priority%20was%20to%20build%20infrastructure%20which%20they%20projected%20as%20a%20development%20model%20in%20the%202014%20elections%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20per%20Jaffrelot%2C%20Modi%20himself%20is%20the%20%E2%80%9Cfourth%20pillar%20of%20the%20Gujarat%20model%E2%80%9D%20as%20he%20continued%20the%20%E2%80%9Cpopulist%20style%20of%20direct%20communications%E2%80%9D%20after%20becoming%20PM.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EJaffrelot%20talked%20about%20how%20Gujarat%20served%20as%20the%20laboratory%20of%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20India%2C%20not%20only%20in%20terms%20of%20%E2%80%9CHindu%20majoritarianism%20but%20also%20of%20caste%20and%20class%20politics%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9C%5BFor%20the%5D%20First%20time%20in%20the%20history%20of%20India%2C%20a%20model%20of%20governance%20invented%20at%20the%20state%20level%20can%20be%20scaled%20up%20to%20the%20national%20dimensions%2C%E2%80%9D%20Jaffrelot%20argues%2C%20pointing%20to%20the%20serious%20consequences%20this%20might%20have%20on%20the%20social%20and%20democratic%20fabric%20of%20India.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EParth%20Pandya%20is%20a%20journalist%20and%20writer%20based%20in%20London.%20Currently%20an%20MA%20candidate%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Westminster%2C%20he%20has%20been%20associated%20with%20organisations%20like%20BBC%20Gujarati.%20He%20tweets%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fparthppandya%5C%22%3E%40parthppandya%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709743551000%2C%22vis