20beyond%20it%20who%20did%20not%20support%20him.%20And%20I%20hope%20he%20does%20that%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%20%E2%80%9CAt%20its%20best%2C%20politics%20is%20about%20bringing%20people%20into%20your%20cause%2C%20not%20turning%20them%20away.%20And%20our%20conservative%20cause%20badly%20needs%20more%20people.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaley%20became%20the%20first%20woman%20to%20become%20governor%20of%20South%20Carolina%2C%C2%A0holding%20office%20from%202011%20to%202017.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20official%20candidates%20for%20both%20the%20Republican%20and%20Democratic%20parties%20are%20chosen%20during%20the%20party%20conventions%20during%20the%C2%A0summer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIncumbent%20Biden%20swept%20the%20Democratic%20primaries%20effectively%20uncontested.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECommenting%20on%20the%20%E2%80%9CSuper%20Tuesday%E2%80%9D%20contest%2C%20he%20said%20American%20people%20are%20facing%20with%20a%20%E2%80%9Cclear%20choice%E2%80%9D%20between%20%E2%80%9Cmoving%20forward%E2%80%9D%20or%20letting%20%E2%80%9CDonald%20Trump%20to%20drag%20us%20backwards%20into%20the%20chaos%2C%20division%2C%20and%20darkness%20that%20defined%20his%20term%20in%20office.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2081-year-old%20leader%20will%20now%20be%20focusing%20on%20his%20crucial%20State%20of%20the%20Union%20speech%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUS%C2%A0voters%20head%20to%C2%A0the%20polls%20to%20elect%20a%20new%20president%20on%20November%205.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fnikki-haley-quits-republican-primaries-with-trump-far-ahead%2Fa-68452647%5C%22%3Earticle%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20originally%20published%20on%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fdw.com%5C%22%3EDW%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709742660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F06215149%2F53462586960_cdf2526205_k.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2F