.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fdharmendra-suffered-injuries-while-dancing-facing-health-issues-for-the-past-two-weeks-but-is-steadily-recovering-report%2Farticleshow%2F108274994.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Election%20Commission%20Quiet%20on%20SBI%20Missing%20SC-Mandated%20Deadline%20for%20Information%20on%20Electoral%20Bonds%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F15125309%2FNirvachan-Sadan-TW.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%3Cspan%3EA%20spokesperson%20for%20the%20Election%20Commission%20has%20said%20it%20has%20%E2%80%9Cno%20information%20or%20comments%20to%20offer%E2%80%9D%20on%20whether%20the%20State%20Bank%20of%20India%20(SBI)%20has%20adhered%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20March%206%20deadline%20for%20giving%20it%20information%20regarding%20electoral%20bonds%20purchased%20and%20encashed%20since%202019.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20is%20no%20word%20on%20if%20the%20Election%20Commission%20has%20approached%20the%20SBI%20for%20information.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Election%20Commission%2C%20the%20finance%20ministry%20and%20the%20law%20ministry%20have%20been%20quiet%20about%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20order%20declaring%20electoral%20bonds%20to%20be%20%E2%80%9Cunconstitutional%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20SBI%20on%20Monday%20(March%205)%20had%20moved%20the%20apex%20court%20seeking%20time%20till%20June%2030%20to%20disclose%20details%20of%20all%20electoral%20bonds%20purchased%20or%20of%20those%20encashed%20by%20political%20parties%2C%20earning%20ire%20and%20disbelief%20about%20India%E2%80%99s%20largest%20public%20sector%20bank%20not%20having%20information%20about%20crores%20of%20rupees%20processed%20by%20it%20going%20into%20political%20parties.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20latest%20to%20sharply%20criticise%20the%20SBI%20is%20the%20bank%20employees%E2%80%99%20trade%20union%2C%20Bank%20Employees%20Federation%20of%20India%20(BEFI)%2C%20which%20said%20the%20state%20bank%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.befi.in%2Fadmin%2FUPL%2FPRESS%2520STAT--2024-03-06.03%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eshould%20adhere%20to%20the%20deadline%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20set%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20BEFI%20consists%20of%20employees%20of%20commercial%20banks%2C%20the%20Reserve%20Bank%20of%20India%2C%20NABARD%2C%20regional%20rural%20banks%20and%20co-operative%20banks.%20The%20union%20said%20that%20public%20sector%20banks%20and%20their%20personnel%20are%20being%20utilised%20for%20the%20%E2%80%9Cnarrow%20political%20interest%20of%20the%20ruling%20forces%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20issued%20a%20scathing%20response%20regarding%20the%20reasons%20the%20SBI%20gave%20while%20asking%20for%20an%20extension%20from%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20reason%20attributed%20by%20%5BIndia%E2%80%99s%5D%20largest%20bank%2C%20%5Bthe%5D%20SBI%20%E2%80%A6%20that%20some%20of%20the%20data%20are%20stored%20in%20physical%20form%20kept%20in%20sealed%20covers%20surprised%20many%20in%20the%20digital%20era%2C%20especially%20in%20%5Bthe%5D%20banking%20sector%2C%20when%20most%20of%20the%20information%20are%20available%20with%20%5Bthe%5D%20click%20of%20a%20mouse%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20union%20said%20in%20its%20statement%20issued%20from%20Kolkata%20and%20signed%20by%20its%20secretary%20S.%20Hari%20Rao.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20also%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9Cof%20late%2C%20it%20is%20observed%20that%20public%20sector%20banks%20and%20its%20personnel%20are%20utilised%20for%20%5Bthe%5D%20narrow%20political%20interest%20of%20the%20ruling%20forces%2C%20like%20in%20the%20cases%20of%20observance%20of%20Partition%20Horrors%20Remembrance%20Day%2C%20Viksit%20Bharat%20Sankalp%20Yatra%20etc.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20express%20our%20strong%20opposition%20to%20such%20activities%20when%20the%20need%20of%20the%20hour%20is%20more%20recruitment%20in%20the%20banking%20industry%20and%20putting%20a%20halt%20to%20looting%20of%20public%20money%20through%20various%20means.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETerming%20the%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20verdict%20on%20electoral%20bonds%20a%20%E2%80%98landmark%E2%80%99%20judgment%2C%20the%20union%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20country%20observed%20that%20%5Bthe%5D%20SBI%20after%2017%20days%20since%20the%20judgement%2C%20moved%20an%20appeal%20to%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20March%204%2C%202024%2C%20just%20two%20days%20before%20the%20deadline%20March%206%2C%202024%2C%20seeking%20time%20up%20to%20June%2030%2C%202024%2C%20to%20comply%20with%20the%20direction%20of%20the%20court%20by%20which%20time%20the%20ensuing%20general%20elections%20will%20be%20over.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20Supreme%20Court%20judge%20Justice%20Deepak%20Gupta%2C%20who%20was%20part%20of%20a%20bench%20in%202019%20that%20ordered%20the%20SBI%20to%20keep%20records%20of%20electoral%20bonds%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsbi-electoral-bonds-ridiculous-deepak-gupta-karan-thapar%5C%22%3Etold%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20earlier%20this%20week%3C%2Fa%3E%20he%20did%20not%20believe%20the%20reason%20the%20SBI%20gave%20while%20asking%20for%20extra%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COnce%20the%20Court%20had%20directed%20that%20you%20keep%20this%20information%20it%20was%20their%20bounden%20duty%20to%20keep%20it%20in%20such%20a%20manner%20that%20when%20a%20Court%20asks%20them%20to%20disclose%20it%20they%20should%20disclose%20it%20as%20early%20as%20possible.%20Not%20that%20they%20take%20months%20to%20disclose%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BEFI%E2%80%99s%20statement%20is%20reproduced%20below%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E6%20March%202024%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPress%20Statement%20issued%20by%20General%20Secretary%2C%20B.E.F.I.%20at%20Kolkata%20on%20SBI%20seeking%20time%20to%20disclose%20details%20of%20electoral%20bonds%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20honourable%20Supreme%20Court%20of%20India%2C%20in%20its%20landmark%20unanimous%20judgement%20on%2015th%20February%202024%20declared%20the%20electoral%20bonds%20scheme%2C%20which%20provided%20blanket%20anonymity%20to%20political%20donors%2C%20as%20unconstitutional%20and%20manifestly%20arbitrary.%20It%20also%20struck%20down%20the%20legal%20amendments%20allowing%20rich%20corporations%20to%20make%20unlimited%20political%20donations%20for%20favours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20directed%20State%20Bank%20of%20India%2C%20sole%20banker%20to%20handle%20electoral%20bond%20through%20only%2029%20designated%20branches%2C%20to%20submit%20full%20details%20of%20contributions%20and%20encashment%20since%20April%202019%20to%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20within%20three%20weeks%20before%206th%20March%202024%20and%20ECI%20to%20publish%20the%20details%20submitted%20by%20SBI%20in%20its%20website%20before%2013th%20March%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20country%20observed%20that%20SBI%20after%2017%20days%20since%20the%20judgement%2C%20moved%20an%20appeal%20to%20Supreme%20Court%20on%204th%20March%202024%2C%20just%20two%20days%20before%20the%20deadline%206th%20March%202024%2C%20seeking%20time%20upto%2030th%20June%202024%20to%20comply%20with%20the%20direction%20of%20the%20court%20by%20which%20time%20the%20ensuing%20General%20Elections%20will%20be%20over.%20The%20reason%20attributed%20by%20the%20India%E2%80%99s%20largest%20Bank%20SBI%20is%20that%20some%20of%20the%20data%20are%20stored%20in%20physical%20form%20kept%20in%20sealed%20covers%20surprised%20many%20in%20the%20digital%20era%20especially%20in%20banking%20sector%20when%20most%20of%20the%20information%20are%20available%20with%20click%20of%20a%20mouse.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20late%2C%20it%20is%20observed%20that%20public%20sector%20banks%20and%20its%20personnel%20are%20utilised%20for%20narrow%20political%20interest%20of%20the%20ruling%20forces%2C%20like%20in%20the%20cases%20of%20observance%20of%20Partition%20Horrors%20Remembrance%20Day%2C%20Viksit%20Bharat%20Sankalp%20Yatra%20etc.%20We%20express%20our%20strong%20opposition%20to%20such%20activities%20when%20need%20of%20the%20hour%20is%20more%20recruitment%20in%20the%20banking%20industry%20and%20put%20halt%20to%20looting%20of%20public%20money%20through%20various%20means.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBank%20Employees%20Federation%20of%20India%20unequivocally%20opposes%20utilisation%20of%20banks%20for%20political%20purposes%20and%20demands%20that%20State%20Bank%20of%20India%20as%20a%20Public%20Sector%20Bank%20should%20disclose%20and%20submit%20all%20the%20details%20of%20electoral%20bonds%20to%20Election%20Commission%20before%20the%20stipulated%20deadline%20of%206th%20March%202024%20as%20directed%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20since%20delayed%20justice%20is%20denial%20of%20justice.%20The%20matter%20is%20pending%20before%20the%20apex%20court%20and%20we%20believe%20that%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20will%20take%20appropriate%20decision%20in%20this%20regard.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHari%20Rao%20S.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESecretary%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709740419000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F15125309%2FNirvachan-Sadan-TW.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Felection-commission-quiet-on-sbi-missing-sc-mandated-deadline-for-information-on-electoral-bonds%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20latest%20to%20take%20issue%20with%20the%20SBI%20for%20its%20seeking%20an%20extension%20till%20end-June%20for%20providing%20data%20on%20electoral%20bonds%20is%20the%20Bank%20Employees%20Federation%20of%20India%2C%20which%20wants%20the%20state%20bank%20to%20adhere%20to%20the%20deadline%20set%20by%20the%20apex%20court.%22%2C%