A%22%E2%80%98Delhi%20Chalo%E2%80%99%20Call%3A%20Unions%20Claim%20Farmers%20Being%20Stopped%20From%20Marching%20to%20Delhi%20in%20Many%20States%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F15202856%2Fimage-1831.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EChandigarh%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Farmers%E2%80%99%20unions%20leading%20the%20%E2%80%98Delhi%20Chalo%E2%80%99%20protest%20since%20February%2013%20claimed%20that%20farmers%20from%20several%20states%20were%20being%20stopped%20from%20marching%20to%20Delhi%20in%20response%20to%20their%20call%20to%20reach%20Delhi%20by%20road%20and%20trains%20starting%20Wednesday%20(March%206).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3ESince%20farmers%20from%20Punjab%20are%20currently%20stuck%20at%20the%20Punjab-Haryana%20due%20to%20excessive%20police%20force%2C%20farmers%20from%20other%20states%20were%20asked%20to%20reach%20Delhi%20by%20any%20means%20possible%20to%20mount%20pressure%20on%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)-led%20Union%20government%20regarding%20their%20key%20demands%2C%20including%20legally%20guaranteed%20minimum%20support%20prices%20(MSP).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3ESarwan%20Singh%20Pandher%2C%20convener%20of%20the%20Kisan%20Mazdoor%20Sangharsh%20Committee%2C%20which%20is%20leading%20the%20Delhi%20Chalo%20protest%20along%20with%20splinter%20groups%20of%20the%20Samyukta%20Kisan%20Morcha%20(which%20played%20a%20key%20role%20in%202020-21%20farmers%E2%80%99%20protest)%2C%20told%20the%20media%20that%20as%20many%20as%20130%20farmers%20were%20detained%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20including%2030%20at%20the%20Sawai%20Madhopur%20railway%20station.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20unable%20to%20contact%20farmers%20coming%20from%20other%20parts%20of%20India%20%5Bincluding%5D%20Bihar%2C%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20as%20well%20as%20southern%20states.%20But%20we%20apprehend%20that%20they%20%E2%80%A6%20may%20have%20been%20detained%20in%20these%20states%20as%20well%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Pandher.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EMany%20states%20that%20Pandher%20mentioned%20are%20BJP-ruled%20states%20which%2C%20according%20to%20Pandher%2C%20have%20increased%20surveillance%20on%20farmers%20marching%20towards%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EPandher%20also%20said%20that%20security%20has%20also%20been%20heightened%20inside%20Delhi%2C%20including%20at%20railway%20and%20bus%20stations%20as%20well%20as%20the%20Jantar%20Mantar%20site%20where%20farmers%20were%20supposed%20to%20gather.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20will%20get%20to%20know%20the%20exact%20situation%20in%20couple%20of%20days%2C%E2%80%9D%20Pandher%20said%20while%20targeting%20the%20Union%20government%20for%20using%20all%20means%20possible%20to%20end%20their%20protest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EHe%20said%20that%20despite%20pressure%2C%20their%20call%20for%20the%20march%20to%20Delhi%20would%20remain%20as%20it%20is.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20will%20not%20return%20unless%20farmers%20get%20a%20legal%20guarantee%20to%20MSP%2C%E2%80%9D%20Pandher%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ESKM%E2%80%99s%20Kisan%20Mazdoor%20Mahapanchayat%20on%20March%2014%20in%20Delhi%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20SKM%2C%20which%20is%20not%20officially%20part%20of%20the%20ongoing%20Delhi%20Chalo%20call%2C%20has%20been%20gearing%20up%20for%20its%20%E2%80%98Kisan%20Mazdoor%20%3Cem%3EMahapanchayat%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20(Hindi%20for%20%E2%80%98great%20council%20of%20farm%20labourers%E2%80%99)%20on%20March%2014%20in%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EAs%20per%20the%20SKM%2C%20the%20upcoming%20mahapanchayat%20will%20focus%20on%20all%20pending%20promises%20the%20BJP%20government%20made%20while%20taking%20back%20the%20three%20controversial%20farm%20laws%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EThe%20promises%20included%20fixing%20MSPs%20based%20on%20a%20formula%20that%20returns%20to%20a%20farmer%20the%20cost%20of%20producing%20a%20crop%20as%20well%20as%20a%20profit%20equalling%2050%25%20that%20amount%2C%20along%20with%20guaranteed%20procurement%2C%20which%20the%20SKM%20claimed%20was%20also%20promised%20in%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%202014%20manifesto%20and%20originally%20recommended%20by%20the%20National%20Farmers%20Commission%20chaired%20by%20M.S.%20Swaminathan%20in%202006.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3ESKM%20member%20Darshan%20Pal%20said%20that%20the%20main%20debate%20on%20MSP%20is%20all%20about%20increasing%20the%20income%20of%20farmers%20and%20then%20rejuvenating%20the%20market%20through%20higher%20farmer%20growth%2C%20but%20the%20Union%20government%20is%20denying%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EThe%20coming%20mahapanchayat%20where%20farmers%20would%20gather%20from%20across%20the%20country%20will%20help%20raising%20the%20issue%20and%20make%20it%20the%20centre-point%20of%20the%20coming%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EOn%20whether%20the%20SKM%20will%20be%20allowed%20permission%20for%20the%20mahapanchayat%2C%20he%20said%20that%20while%20they%20have%20already%20applied%20for%20permission%20with%20the%20Delhi%20government%20as%20well%20as%20the%20home%20affairs%20ministry%2C%20he%20personally%20believed%20that%20the%20ministry%20may%20deny%20it%20permission%20given%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20strong%20resistance%20to%20public%20protests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CWe%E2%80%99ll%20get%20to%20know%20the%20exact%20status%20in%20couple%20of%20days.%20In%20case%20we%20are%20not%20allowed%20to%20hold%20a%20mahapanchyat%20in%20Delhi%2C%20we%20will%20take%20a%20fresh%20call%20and%20decide%20a%20future%20course%20of%20action%20through%20a%20meeting%20before%20March%2014%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EThe%20SKM%20has%20also%20strongly%20protested%20and%20condemned%20the%20BJP%20for%20fielding%20Ajay%20Mishra%20Teni%20from%20Uttar%20Pradesh%E2%80%99s%20Kheri%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3ETeni%20is%20the%20father%20of%20Ashish%20Mishra%20Teni%2C%20who%20is%20the%20main%20accused%20in%20a%202021%20incident%20where%20he%20along%20with%20others%20allegedly%20mowed%20to%20death%20four%20farmers%20protesting%20in%20Lakhimpur%20Kheri.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EThe%20SKM%20has%20also%20called%20the%20senior%20Teni%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Findia%2Ffarmers-workers-to-mark-black-day-on-tuesday-to-seek-ajay-mishra-tenis-dismissal-over-lakhimpur-kheri-killings-2709235%5C%22%3Ea%20%E2%80%9Cchief%20conspirator%E2%80%9D%20behind%20the%20incident%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709734234000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F15202856%2Fimage-1831.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Ffarmers-unions-claim-farmers-from-many-states-prevented-from-marching-to-delhi%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Meanwhile%2C%20the%20influential%20umbrella%20body%20Samyukta%20Kisan%20Morcha%2C%20which%20is%20not%20officially%20part%20of%20the%20ongoing%20Delhi%20Chalo%20call%2C%20has%20been%20gearing%20up%20for%20its%20%E2%80%98Kisan%20Mazdoor%20Mahapanchayat%E2%80%99%20in%20Delhi%20on%20March%2014.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Ffarmers-unions-claim-farmers-from-many-states-prevented-from-marching-to-delhi%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bengal%20Cops%20Hand%20Over%20Sandeshkhali%20Strongman%20To%20CBI%20After%20Court%20Reprimand%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ESuspended%20Trinamool%20leader%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fsheikh-shahjahan%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESheikh%20Shahjahan%3C%2Fa%3E%20-%20the%20key%20accused%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fsandeshkhali%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESandeshkhali%3C%2Fa%3E%20extortion%2C%20land%20grab%2C%20and%20sexual%20assault%20cases%20-%20was%20transferred%20to%20the%20custody%20of%20the%20CBI%20Wednesday%20evening%2C%20capping%20a%20two-day%20stand-off%20between%20the%20Bengal%20government%20and%20the%20central%20agency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday%20the%20Calcutta%20High%20Court%20had%20ordered%20the%20state%20to%20hand%20over%20Shahjahan%2C%20and%20all%20case%20materials%2C%20to%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation.%20The%20state%20was%20given%20till%204.30%20pm%20but%20refused%20to%20comply%2C%20citing%20a%20last-gasp%20appeal%20at%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20which%20had%20refused%20an%20urgent%20hearing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20CBI%20team%20reached%20Bengal%20Police's%20HQ%20in%20Kolkata%2C%20they%20were%20forced%20to%20return%20empty-handed.%20They%20were%20told%20Shahjahan%20would%20remain%20in%20police%20custody%20till%20the%20Supreme%20Court's%20ruling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhand-over-shahjahan-sheikh-to-cbi-today-high-court-to-bengal-government-5180345%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBengal%2C%20CBI%20In%20Stand-Off%20Over%20Shahjahan%2C%20Supreme%20Court%20Moved%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20afternoon%2C%20an%20irate%20High%20Court%20set%20a%20new%20deadline%20-%204.15%20pm.%20The%20court%20underlined%20the%20seriousness%20of%20the%20state%20disregarding%20an%20order%20passed%20by%20Chief%20Justice%20TS%20Sivagnanam%2C%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BSupreme%20Court%20has%20not%20ordered%20a%20stay.%20So%20Shahjahan%20must%20be%20handed%20over%20to%20the%20CBI%20by%204.15%20pm...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20High%20Court%20also%20issued%20a%20notice%20of%20contempt%20and%20asked%20Bengal%20Police's%20Criminal%20Investigation%20Department%2C%20which%20had%20custody%20of%20Sheikh%20Shahjahan%2C%20to%20file%20an%20affidavit%20within%20two%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbengal-government-directed-to-hand-over-sheikh-shahjahan-to-cbi-by-4-15-pm-5186826%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECBI%20Team%20At%20Bengal%20Police%20HQ%20For%20Shahjahan%20As%20Deadline%20Ends%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20yesterday's%20hearing%20the%20High%20Court%20held%20the%20police%20to%20be%20%26quot%3Btotally%20biased%26quot%3B%20and%20called%20for%20a%20%26quot%3Bfair%2C%20honest%2C%20and%20complete%20investigation%26quot%3B%20into%20allegations%20against%20Shahjahan.%20%26quot%3BThere%20can%20be%20no%20better%20case%20than%20this...%20which%20requires%20to%20be%20transferred%20(and)%20to%20be%20investigated%20by%20the%20CBI%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20observed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESheikh%20Shahjahan%20went%20on%20the%20run%20on%20January%205%2C%20the%20day%20a%20mob%20of%20his%20supporters%20attacked%20an%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20team.%20Nearly%20two%20months%20later%2C%20he%20was%20arrested%20-%20three%20days%20after%20the%20state's%20stand-off%2C%20this%20time%20with%20the%20High%20Court%20-%20and%20suspended%20from%20the%20Trinamool%20for%20six%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftrinamool-congress-leader-sheikh-shahjahan-main-accused-in-sandeshkhali-case-arrested-say-sources-5147488%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESandeshkhali%20Accused%20Shahjahan%2C%20On%20The%20Run%20For%2055%20Days%2C%20Arrested%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20High%20Court%20on%20Tuesday%20ruled%20on%20separate%20pleas%20-%20from%20the%20ED%20and%20the%20state%20government%20-%20to%20its%20earlier%20order%20on%20the%20setting%