d%20him%20to%20be%20more%20careful%20and%20cautious%20in%20future%2C%26quot%3B%20PTI%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20commission%20has%20further%20directed%20Gandhi%2C%20as%20a%20star%20campaigner%2C%20to%20take%20into%20notice%20its%20March%201%20advisory%20for%20all%20parties%2C%20star%20campaigners%20and%20candidates%20in%20right%20earnest%20while%20making%20public%20utterances.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20poll%20panel%20issued%20a%20notice%20to%20Mr%20Gandhi%20on%20November%2023%20seeking%20his%20stand%20on%20his%20speeches%20during%20his%20campaigns%20for%20the%20assembly%20elections%20in%20Rajasthan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20Congress%20president%20took%20the%20%26quot%3Bpickpocket%26quot%3B%20dig%20at%20Modi%20during%20his%20poll%20speech%2C%20alleging%20that%20the%20prime%20minister%20diverts%20people's%20attention%20while%20industrialist%20Gautam%20Adani%20picks%20their%20pockets.%20This%20is%20how%20pickpockets%20operate%2C%20he%20had%20alleged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20order%20followed%20a%20petition%20that%20had%20also%20objected%20to%20certain%20other%20statements%20by%20Mr%20Gandhi%20referring%20to%20the%20prime%20minister%20as%20%26quot%3Bpanauti%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709732940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2F1hs0sdj8_rahul-gandhi_625x300_05_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbe-more-careful-election-commission-of-india-to-rahul-gandhi-on-panauti-jibe-at-pm-modi-5188280%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20(ECI)%20asked%20Congress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20to%20be%20more%20careful%20and%20cautious%20in%20his%20public%20utterances%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20his%20%26quot%3Bpanauti%26quot%3B%20(bad%20omen)%20and%20%26quot%3Bpickp