red%20on%20the%20app%20will%20get%20%E2%80%9Cmerchandise%2C%20refreshments%2C%20and%20certificates.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20reached%20out%20to%20professor%20Meena%2C%20principal%20of%20Kalindi%20College%2C%20whose%20name%20and%20photo%20is%20also%20on%20the%20poster.%20The%20story%20will%20be%20updated%20if%20and%20when%20a%20response%20is%20received.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20poster%20was%20shared%20by%20Naveen%20Gaur%2C%20faculty%20at%20Delhi%20University%E2%80%99s%20Dyal%20Singh%20College.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F06164243%2Fimage-1910.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22818%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F06164243%2Fimage-1910.png%20610w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F06164243%2Fimage-1910-215x300.png%20215w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-700445%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221143%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharing%20the%20poster%2C%20Gaur%20wrote%20that%20the%20issue%20is%20that%20the%20poster%20mandates%20participants%20to%20register%20on%20the%20NaMo%20app.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20could%20be%20that%20some%20people%20want%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20activity%20but%20may%20not%20want%20to%20register%20on%20the%20NaMo%20app.%20Yes%2C%20DU%20rules%20mandate%20that%20the%20information%20about%20the%20participants%20should%20be%20provided%20beforehand%20and%20this%20can%20be%20done%20without%20registering%20on%20the%20NaMo%20app.%20Such%20directives%20from%20DU%20should%20be%20avoided%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.narendramodi.in%2Fen%2Fmobile%2Fprivacy-policy%23%3A~%3Atext%3DCollaboration%252C%2520community%252Dbuilding%2520and%2520connecting%2C%2526%2520grass%252Droot%2520workers%2520themselves.%5C%22%3Eprivacy%20policy%20%3C%2Fa%3Eof%20the%20NaMo%20app%20community%20states%20the%20following%3A%20%E2%80%9CCollaboration%2C%20community-building%20and%20connecting%20with%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20are%20the%20main%20pillars%20of%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20App%20i.e.%20NaMo%20App.%20(%E2%80%98App%E2%80%99).%20The%20NaMo%20App%20is%20a%20%E2%80%98one%20of%20its%20kind%E2%80%99%20app%20which%20is%20powered%20by%20supporters%20%26amp%3B%20fans%20of%20PM%20Modi%2C%20volunteers%20%26amp%3B%20grass-root%20workers%20themselves.%20You%20are%20joining%20millions%20of%20users%20of%20this%20community%20who%20aspire%20for%20a%20New%20India.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20states%20that%20the%20app%20allows%20users%20to%20%E2%80%9Cinteract%20directly%20with%20PM%20Modi%2C%20contribute%20to%20nation%20building%20through%20various%20ways%20and%20connect%20with%20different%20communities%20such%20as%20%E2%80%98Exam%20Warriors%E2%80%99.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20NaMo%20App%20keeps%20you%20updated%20about%20the%20initiatives%20and%20achievements%20of%20the%20government%20led%20by%20PM%20Modi.%20You%20can%20also%20connect%20with%20fellow%20volunteers%20and%20organise%20various%20events%20and%20initiatives.%20You%20can%20take%20part%20in%20different%20surveys%20and%20various%20movements%20like%20%E2%80%98Fit%20India%E2%80%99%2C%20%E2%80%98Sankalp%20Se%20Siddhi%E2%80%99%2C%20%E2%80%98I%20Am%20New%20India%E2%80%99%2C%20%E2%80%98Swachh%20Bharat%E2%80%99%20etc.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20provide%20%E2%80%9Ca%20tailor-made%20and%20personalised%20experience%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20information%20shared%20on%20the%20app%20%E2%80%9Cmaybe%20processed%20and%20analysed%20by%20third%20party%20services%20who%20are%20engaged%20by%20us%20with%20due%20confidentiality%20obligations%20and%20solely%20for%20the%20specific%20purpose%20of%20such%20services%E2%80%9D%2C%20says%20the%20privacy%20policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20will%20help%20the%20app%20give%20you%20the%20best%20possible%20experience%20by%20showing%20content%20in%20your%20language%20and%20according%20to%20your%20interests.%20For%20example%2C%20based%20on%20the%20location%20data%20collected%2C%20you%20may%20get%20a%20push%20notification%20when%20PM%20Modi%20is%20in%20your%20state%20or%20%5Bwhen%5D%20there%20is%20an%20important%20initiative%20or%20event%20happening%20in%20your%20state.%20Similarly%2C%20based%20on%20your%20previous%20interactions%20within%20the%20app%2C%20you%20may%20receive%20push%20notifications%20based%20on%20your%20interests%20in%20the%20future%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20a%20%E2%80%9Ccovert%20election%20campaign%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Nandita%20Narain%2C%20former%20president%20of%20DUTA%20and%20FEDCUTA%2C%20and%20president%20of%20the%20Democratic%20Teachers%E2%80%99%20Front%2C%20and%20chairperson%20of%20the%20Joint%20Forum%20for%20Movement%20on%20Education.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20a%20covert%20election%20campaign%20and%20mandatory%20participation%20makes%20it%20coercive.%20All%20our%20(Delhi%20University)%20official%20spaces%20are%20being%20used%20for%20such%20activities%20and%20such%20use%20on%20the%20eve%20of%20the%20general%20elections%20is%20highly%20inappropriate%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20June%20last%20year%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20while%20addressing%20the%20Delhi%20University%20during%20its%20centenary%20celebrations%2C%20had%20said%20that%20the%20institution%20should%20make%20India%20%E2%80%9CViksit%20Bharat%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20goal%20of%20Delhi%20University%20should%20be%20to%20make%20India%20%E2%80%98Viksit%20Bharat%E2%80%99%20(developed%20India)%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Fdelhi%2Fgoal-of-delhi-university-should-be-to-make-india-viksit-bharat-pm-modi-8694718%2F%5C%22%3Ehad%20said.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20standard%20operating%20procedures%20for%20universities%20on%20Delhi%20University%E2%80%99s%20Viksit%20Bharat%202047%20page%20say%20that%E2%80%9D%E2%80%98Viksit%20Bharat%402047%20is%20the%20vision%20of%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20to%20make%20India%20a%20developed%20nation%20by%202047%2C%20the%20100th%20year%20of%20its%20independence.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20urges%20the%20participation%20of%20the%20youth%2C%20and%20also%20says%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9CDepartment%20of%20Higher%20Education%2C%20Ministry%20of%20Education%20will%20lead%20the%20communication%20and%20outreach%20in%20this%20regard.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709731858000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F01%2F27162303%2Fnamo-app-1.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fdus-kalindi-college-asks-students-to-register-on-namo-app-for-event-with-smriti-irani-as-chief-guest%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20poster%20by%20Kalindi%20College%20says%20that%20registration%20on%20the%20app%20is%20mandatory%20and%20only%20those%20students%20who%20have%20registered%20on%20the%20app%20will%20get%20%E2%80%9Cmerchandise%2C%20refreshments%2C%20and%20certificates.%E2%80%9D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A23%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fdus-kalindi-college-asks-students-to-register-on-namo-app-for-event-with-smriti-irani-as-chief-guest%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Pakistan's%20Ex-PM%20Zulfikar%20Ali%20Bhutto%2C%20Hanged%20in%201979%2C%20Didn%E2%80%99t%20Get%20a%20Fair%20Trial%2C%20Rules%20SC%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F29103805%2FSupreme_Court_of_Pakistan2.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20Supreme%20Court%20ruled%20on%20Wednesday%20(March%206)%20that%20former%20Prime%20Minister%20Zulfikar%20Ali%20Bhutto%2C%20who%20was%20hanged%20in%201979%20after%20being%20convicted%20of%20murder%2C%20didn%E2%80%99t%20get%20a%20fair%20trial.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20didn%E2%80%99t%20find%20that%20the%20fair%20trial%20and%20due%20process%20requirements%20were%20met%2C%E2%80%9D%20Reuters%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Fasia-pacific%2Fpakistans-bhutto-hanged-44-years-ago-didnt-get-fair-trial-rules-top-court-2024-03-06%2F%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20Chief%20Justice%20Qazi%20Faez%20Isa%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20nine-member%20bench%20led%20by%20Isa%20consisted%20of%20Justice%20Sardar%20Tariq%20Masood%2C%20Justice%20Syed%20Mansoor%20Ali%20Shah%2C%20Justice%20Yahya%20Afridi%2C%20Justice%20Amin-ud-Din%20Khan%2C%20Justice%20Jamal%20Khan%20Mandokhel%2C%20Justice%20Muhammad%20Ali%20Mazhar%2C%20Justice%20Syed%20Hasan%20Azhar%20Rizvi%20and%20Justice%20Musarrat%20Hilali.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20proceedings%20were%20broadcast%20live%20on%20the%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.supremecourt.gov.pk%2Fcourt-proceedings%2F%5C%22%3Ewebsite%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DxVHE-F62J3M%5C%22%3EYouTube%3C%2Fa%3E%20channel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20announcing%20the%20unanimous%20opinion%2C%20%3Cem%3EDawn%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dawn.com%2Fnews%2F1819573%2Fsc-says-conditions-of-fair-trial-due-process-not-met-in-zulfikar-bhuttos-trial%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20Chief%20Justice%20Isa%20as%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20proceedings%20of%20the%20trial%20by%20the%20Lahore%20High%20Court%20and%20of%20the%20appeal%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20of%20Pakistan%20do%20not%20meet%20the%20requirements%20of%20the%20fundamental%20right%20to%20a%20fair%20trial%20and%20due%20process%20enshrined%20in%20Articles%204%20and%209%20of%20the%20Constitution%2C%20and%20later%20guaranteed%20as%20a%20separate%20and%20fundamental%20right%20under%20Article%2010A%20of%20the%20Constitution.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20newspaper%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20acknowledged%20that%20there%20had%20been%20%E2%80%9Csome%20cases%20in%20our%20judicial%20history%20that%20created%20a%20public%20perception%20that%20either%20fear%20or%20favour%20deterred%20the%20performance%20of%20a%20duty%20to%20administer%20justice%20in%20accordance%20with%20the%20law%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20must%20therefore%20be%20willing%20to%20confront%20our%20past%20missteps%20and%20fallibilities%20with%20humility%2C%20in%20the%20spirit%20of%20self-accountability%2C%20and%20as%20a%20testament%20to%20our%20commitment%20to%20ensure%20that%20justice%20must%20be%20served%20with%20unwavering%20integrity%20and%20fidelity%20to%20the%20law%2C%E2%80%9D%20Justice%20Isa%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20cannot%20correct%20ourselves%20and%20progress%20in%20the%20right%20direction%20until%20we%20acknowledge%20our%20past%20mistakes%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20question%20of%20whether%20the%20awarding%20and%20maintaining%20of%20the%20death%20sentence%20was%20%E2%80%9Cjustified%20or%20could%20amount%20to%20deliberate%20murder%E2%80%9D%2C%20Chief%20Justice%20Isa%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CThis%20court%20cannot%20reappraise%20the%20evidence%20and%20undo%20the%20decision%20of%20the%20case.%20However%2C%20in%20our%20detailed%20reasons%2C%20we%20shall%20identify%20the%20major%20constitutional%20and%20legal%20lapses%20that%20had%20occurred%20with%20regard%20to%20fair%20trial%20and%20due%20process.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20will%20issue%20a%20detailed%20order%20later%2C%20per%20news%20reports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBhutto%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20the%20Pakistan%20Peoples%20Party%20(PPP)%20now%20run%20by%20his%20grandson%20and%20former%20foreign%20minister%20Bilawal%20Bhutto%20Zardari%2C%20was%20hanged%20in%201979%20after%20a%20trial%20under%20the%20military%20regime%20of%20late%20General%20Zia-ul-Haq.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Shehbaz%20Sharif%20hailed%20the%20ruling.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20a%20positive%20development%20that%20a%20wrong%20done%20by%20a%20court%20has%20been%20corrected%20by%20a%20court%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20from%20his%20office%2C%20reported%20Reuters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20pursuit%20of%20justice%20was%20a%20labour%20of%20love%20by%20President%20Asif%20Ali%20Zardari%20in%20the%20name%20of%20his%20wife%20Shaheed%20Mohtarma%20Benazir%20Bhutto.%20Our%20family%20waited%203%20generations%20to%20hear%20these%20words.%20Jiya%20Bhutto!%20Long%20live%20Bhutto!%E2%80%9D%20Bhutto%20Zardari%20said%20later%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-media-max-width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EMore%20than%2044%20years%20after%20judicial%20murder%20and%20more%20than%2012%20years%20after%20presidential%20reference%20was%20filed%3B%20today%20a%20unanimous%20decision%20announce%20by%20CJP%20Isa.%20Shaheed%20Zulfikar%20Ali%20Bhutto%20did%20not%20get%20a%20fair%20trial.%20The%20pursuit%20of%20justice%20was%20a%20labour%20of%20love%20by%20President%20Asif%20Ali%20Zardari%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FrTNgLWeood%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FrTNgLWeood%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20BilawalBhuttoZardari%20(%40BBhuttoZardari)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FBBhuttoZardari%2Fstatus%2F1765281795417706802%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMarch%206%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20hoped%20that%2C%2044%20years%20later%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20opinion%20would%20allow%20Pakistan%20to%20progress%2C%20and%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9Csystem%E2%80%9D%20would%20finally%20be%20put%20on%20the%20right%20path%2C%20reported%20%3Cem%3EDawn%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20stain%20of%20this%20decision%20made%20it%20difficult%20for%20the%20people%20of%20Pakistan%20to%20have%20faith%20in%20the%20court%2C%20and%20get%20justice%20from%20this%20court%2C%20especially%20if%20someone%20like%20the%20prime%20minister%20did%20not%20get%20justice%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709731184000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F29103805%2FSupreme_Court_of_Pakistan2.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fpakistans-ex-pm-zulfikar-ali-bhutto-hanged-in-1979-didnt-get-a-fair-trial-rules-sc%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22'We%20didn't%20find%20that%20the%20fair%20trial%20and%20due%20process%20requirements%20were%20met%2C'%20said%20Chief%20Justice%20Qazi%20Faez%20Isa.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A14%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fpakistans-ex-pm-zulfikar-ali-bhutto-hanged-in-1979-didnt-get-a-fair-trial-rules-sc%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Flood%20Gaza%20With%20Aid%E2%80%99%3A%20UN%20Calls%20on%20International%20Community%20as%20Children%20Die%20From%20Starvation%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F20163806%2Fimage1170x530croppe.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%E2%80%9CWith%20children%20starting%20%E2%80%A6%20to%20die%20from%20starvation%2C%20that%20should%20be%20an%20alarm%20like%20no%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eother%2C%E2%80%9D%20Jens%20Laerke%2C%20spokesman%20for%20the%20UN%20humanitarian%20agency%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.un.org%2Fen%2Fstory%2F2024%2F03%2F1147227%5C%22%3Etold%3C%2Fa%3E%20reporters%20in%20Geneva.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Hamas-run%20health%20ministry%20in%20Gaza%20reported%20that%2015%20children%20succumbed%20to%20starvation%20in%20a%20single%20hospital.%20The%20UN%20has%20grimly%20acknowledged%20the%20looming%20inevitability%20of%20famine%20in%20the%20territory%2C%20which%20has%20been%20under%20assault%20since%20October%207.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELast%20weekend%2C%20the%20WHO%20revealed%20distressing%20scenes%20of%20starving%20children%20after%20gaining%20access%20to%20two%20northern%20hospitals%20for%20the%20first%20time%20since%20October.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20Kamal%20Adwan%20hospital%2C%20the%20only%20pediatric%20facility%20in%20northern%20Gaza%2C%20doctors%20reported%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.france24.com%2Fen%2Flive-news%2F20240305-gaza-s-starving-children-need-a-flood-of-aid-un%5C%22%3Eat%20least%2010%20children%20had%20died%20due%20to%20starvation%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20according%20to%20Ahmed%20Dahir%2C%20who%20headed%20the%20mission.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20health%20ministry%20later%20updated%20the%20number%20of%20child%20deaths%20at%20the%20hospital%20to%2015%2C%20with%20an%20additional%20six%20acutely%20malnourished%20infants%20in%20critical%20condition.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELaerke%20pleaded%20for%20immediate%20action%2C%20urging%20the%20international%20community%20to%20%E2%80%9Cflood%20Gaza%20with%20aid%E2%80%9D%20to%20alleviate%20the%20growing%20humanitarian%20crisis.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBefore%20the%20latest%20escalation%20in%20Gaza%2C%20around%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.un.org%2Fen%2Fstory%2F2024%2F03%2F1147227%5C%22%3E500%20trucks%20a%20day%20entered%20Gaza%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20the%20daily%20tally%20in%20recent%20months%20and%20days%20has%20barely%20risen%20above%20133%2C%20Laerke%20explained.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20UN%20assessment%20in%20January%20revealed%20alarming%20levels%20of%20malnutrition%20among%20children%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMalnutrition%20%E2%80%93%20which%20leads%20to%20irreparable%20wasting%20in%20young%20children%20%E2%80%93%20was%20never%20the%20deadly%20threat%20in%20Gaza%20that%20it%20is%20now%2C%20as%20the%20enclave%20was%20largely%20self-sufficient%20in%20fish%20and%20other%20food%20production%2C%20WHO%E2%80%99s%20Dr.%20Rik%20Peeperkorn%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CBefore%20the%20recent%20months%E2%80%99%20hostilities%2C%20wasting%20in%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%20was%20rare%20with%20just%200.8%25%20of%20children%20under%20five%20years%20of%20age%20acutely%20malnourished%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explained.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20(current)%20rate%20of%2015.6%25%20of%20wasting%20among%20children%20under%20two%20in%20northern%20Gaza%20suggests%20a%20serious%20and%20rapid%20decline.%20Such%20a%20decline%20in%20a%20population%E2%80%99s%20nutritional%20status%20in%20three%20months%20is%20unprecedented%20globally%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.un.org%2Fen%2Fstory%2F2024%2F03%2F1147227%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20WHO%20official%20noted%20with%20concern%20that%2090%25%20of%20children%20under%20two%20years%20old%20and%2095%25%20of%20pregnant%20and%20breastfeeding%20women%20%E2%80%9Cface%20severe%20food%20poverty%20%E2%80%93%20meaning%20they%20have%20consumed%20two%20or%20less%20food%20groups%20in%20the%20previous%20day%20%E2%80%93%20and%20the%20food%20they%20do%20have%20access%20to%20is%20of%20the%20lowest%20nutritional%20value%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709730048000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F20163806%2Fimage1170x530croppe.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fflood-gaza-with-aid-un-calls-on-international-community-as-children-die-from-starvation%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Last%20weekend%2C%20the%20WHO%20revealed%20distressing%20scenes%20of%20starving%20children%20a