s%20necklace%20and%20how%20much%20the%20three%20Khans%20charged%20for%20shaking%20their%20legs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBeyond%20this%20titillation%2C%20you%20have%20helped%20the%20middle%20classes%20absorb%20a%20few%20lessons.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFirst%2C%20we%20should%20all%20be%20so%20ever%20grateful%20to%20you%20for%20demonstrating%20that%20someone%20is%20higher%20than%20the%20Indian%20state.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20have%20all%20thought%20that%20under%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%2C%20the%20Indian%20state%20had%20become%20all%20too%20omnipotent%20and%20omnipresent%20as%20it%20has%20performed%20an%20unending%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Epranprathista%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20at%20the%20Church%20of%20National%20Security.%20The%20archbishops%20of%20this%20church%20have%20claimed%20for%20themselves%20the%20right%20to%20make%20more%20intrusive%20and%20more%20absolutist%20demands%20over%20our%20lives%20and%20liberties%3B%20but%2C%20the%20ease%20with%20which%20Jamnagar%20airport%20was%20re-designated%20to%20accommodate%20your%20guests%20from%20all%20around%20the%20world%20proves%20that%20concepts%C2%A0%20like%20%E2%80%9Cnational%20security%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cnational%20defence%E2%80%9D%20are%20really%20flexible%20constructs.%20Next%20time%20when%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fa-timeline-of-umar-khalids-bail-hearings%5C%22%3EUmar%20Khalid%E2%80%99s%20bail%20application%20comes%20up%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20their%20Lordships%20would%20do%20well%20to%20apply%20the%20Jamnagar%20rules.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESecond%2C%20bringing%20Rihanna%20was%20a%20nice%20touch.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShe%20may%20or%20may%20not%20be%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Frihanna-farmers-protest-tweet-mea%5C%22%3Einfamous%20%E2%80%98IT%20cell%E2%80%99%20blacklist%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20those%20who%20have%20to%20be%20mer