their%20customers%2C%20says%20that%20the%20hair%20oil%20and%20shampoo%20have%20had%20a%20tremendous%20impact%20for%20her.%20She%20faced%20hairfall%20issues%20as%20she%20is%20peri-menopausal%20and%20has%20thyroid%20issues.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20tried%20many%20different%20products%20over%20the%20years%20but%20nothing%20really%20worked.%20I%20found%20out%20about%20Nidhi%E2%80%99s%20Grandmaa%20Secret%20through%20a%20friend%20and%20have%20been%20using%20it%20for%20five%20months%20now.%20I%20have%20seen%20a%20noticeable%20difference%20in%20my%20hair%2C%20my%20hair%20fall%20has%20greatly%20reduced.%20My%20son%2C%20too%2C%20uses%20it%20and%20has%20seen%20good%20results%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Kamaljeet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20almost%20six%20months%2C%20the%20duo%20just%20worked%20on%20fulfilling%20orders.%20There%20would%20be%20oil%20simmering%20on%20the%20gas%20morning%2C%20afternoon%20and%20evening%3B%20with%20its%20shelf%20life%20of%20three%20years.%20As%20orders%20crossed%20almost%20300%20per%20day%2C%20they%20knew%20that%20it%20could%20no%20longer%20be%20managed%20from%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20looked%20for%20manufacturing%20facilities.%20They%20had%20a%20caveat%20though%20%E2%80%93%20it%20had%20to%20be%20handmade.%20While%20many%20refused%2C%20they%20found%20one%20in%20Panchkula%2C%20where%20they%20replicated%20the%20setup%2C%20where%20more%20than%2050%20women%20manufacture%20the%20oil.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20hero%20product%20of%20Nidhi%E2%80%99s%20Grandmaa%20Secret%20is%20the%20%E2%80%98anti-hairfall%E2%80%99%20oil%2C%20priced%20at%20Rs%20499%20for%20a%20100%20ml%20bottle%2C%20followed%20by%20the%20curry%20leaf%20and%20hibiscus%20shampoo%20which%20is%20priced%20at%20Rs%20449%20for%20a%20200%20ml%20bottle.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENidhi%20and%20Rajni%20recently%20moved%20into%20an%20office%20and%20are%20looking%20to%20expand%20their%20team.%20The%20two%20mothers%20also%20plan%20to%20launch%20more%20natural%20hair%20care%20products