0a%20deal%20for%20Rs%202%20crore%20from%20three%20%E2%80%98Sharks%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20Anupam%20Mittal%2C%20Vineeta%20Singh%2C%20and%20Amit%20Jain.%20Post%20their%20appearance%20on%20Shark%20Tank%2C%20they%20have%20received%20over%2020%2C000%20queries%20from%20retailers%20and%20distributors%20in%20just%2010%20days%2C%20say%20the%20elated%20founders%2C%20adding%20that%20they%20want%20to%20increase%20their%20online%20presence%20in%20the%20coming%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20initially%20keeping%20their%20venture%20a%20secret%20from%20their%20families%20to%20establishing%20a%20company%20valued%20at%20Rs%20200%20crore%2C%20Avneet%20and%20Saket%20exemplify%20the%20power%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F340982%2Fiit-delhi-graduates-aroleap-x-fitness-home-gym-smart-ai-strength-training-equipment-innovation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehard%20work%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20seizing%20opportunities%20at%20the%20right%20time%2C%20and%20embodying%20the%20hustle%20culture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20need%20to%20be%20honest%20with%20yourself%20and%20your%20customers%2C%20work%20hard%2C%20and%20have%20the%20zeal%20to%20build%20a%20business.%20Don%E2%80%99t%20stick%20to%20a%20strategy%3B%20instead%2C%20be%20willing%20to%20redo%20things%20if%20something%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20work.%20We%20achieved%20our%20goals%20because%20our%20intent%20and%20passion%20were%20strong%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Avneet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESources%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fweee-forum.org%2Fws_news%2Fof-16-billion-mobile-phones-possessed-worldwide-5-3-billion-will-become-waste-in-2022%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EWEEE%20Forum%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E