281.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FTiger-2-2-1709384375-768x432.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FTiger-2-2-1709384375-150x84.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-343744%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22720%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EA%20picture%20of%20the%20tiger%20ready%20to%20hunt%2C%20captured%20by%20smart%20AI%20cameras%20during%20the%20night%20time%20got%20distracted%20by%20the%20hooters%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Valiance%20%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20stories%20hold%20personal%20meaning%20for%20Kathait%20who%20grew%20up%20in%20Dehradun%20near%20a%20famed%20tiger%20reserve.%20He%20would%20often%20hear%20heart-wrenching%20stories%20of%20locals%20being%20mauled%20to%20death.%20Being%20able%20to%20now%20be%20a%20part%20of%20a%20smart%20solution%20is%20a%20victory%20for%20him.%20It%20isn%E2%80%99t%20just%20about%20protecting%20humans%2C%20but%20also%20wildlife%2C%20he%20emphasises.%20As%20a%20testament%20to%20Valiance%E2%80%99s%20commitment%20to%20using%20AI%20for%20social%20good%2C%20the%20Wildlife%20Eye%20is%20community-centric%20in%20that%20it%20prioritises%20local%20community%20benefits.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElaborating%20on%20this%2C%20Kathait%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20value%20of%20human%20life%20is%20immeasurable%2C%20and%20assigning%20a%20numerical%20figure%20to%20it%20is%20beyond%20consideration.%20The%20loss%20of%20human%20lives%20or%20livestock%20in%20animal%20attacks%20not%20only%20bears%20a%20substantial%20financial%20burden%20on%20the%20exchequer%20running%20into%20crores%2C%20but%20it%20also%20creates%20social%20unrest.%20Our%20solution%20endeavours%20to%20avert%20such%20incidents%2C%20thereby%20enhancing%20overall%20safety%20and%20mitigating%20the%20economic%20and%20emotional%20toll%20associated%20with%20these%20unfortunate%20events.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThou