0villagers%20to%20collect%20and%20segregate%20dry%20and%20wet%20waste%20at%20the%20household%20level.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSo%2C%20the%20waste%20that%20would%20earlier%20be%20thrown%20out%20in%20public%20spaces%20earlier%2C%20is%20now%20being%20converted%20into%20vermicompost.%20Every%20month%2C%20we%20are%20able%20to%20convert%20at%20least%2050%20kg%20of%20waste%20and%20sell%20its%20compost%20to%20farmers%20in%20and%20nearby%20our%20village.%20So%20far%2C%20we%20have%20earned%20Rs%2010%20lakh%20in%20the%20past%203-4%20years%20with%20waste.%20We%20have%20also%20earned%20Rs%2070%2C000%20by%20selling%20plastic%20waste%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Meenakshi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20profits%2C%20the%20model%20village%20has%20also%20installed%20two%20rooftop%20solar%20grids%20to%20produce%206%20kilovolt%20of%20electricity%2C%20making%20the%20village%20energy%20self-sufficient.%20%E2%80%9COver%20the%20years%2C%20we%20installed%20solar%20lights%20in%20the%20village%20schools%2C%20anganwadis%2C%20roads%2C%20and%20gram%20panchayat.%20This%20has%20reduced%20monthly%20power%20bills%20expenses%20of%20Rs%2015%2C000%20for%20our%20gram%C2%A0panchayat.%20Now%2C%20we%20get%20zero%20power%20bill%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20than%20this%2C%20Meenakshi%20has%20helped%20the%20village%20get%201%2C000%20tap%20water%20connections%20under%20the%20Har%20Ghar%20Jal%20mission%20of%20the%20central%20government.%20She%20has%20also%20roped%20in%20the%20community%20to%20plant%201%20lakh%20fruit-bearing%20trees%20on%20the%20roadside%2C%20promoted%20usage%20of%20eco-friendly%20cutlery%20in%20weddings%2C%20set%20up%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F310032%2Fias-officer-himanshu-kafaltia-sets-up-libraries-in-villages-in-uttarakhand%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edigital%20library%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20deployed%20a%20free%20school%20bus%20to%20pick%20and%20drop%20school-going%20childre